Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2022 Kia Carnival SX. This exceptional minivan boasts a captivating exterior in Aurora Black, complemented by a spacious and meticulously designed interior that combines style and functionality.

Highlighted features include:
• Handsfree Bluetooth
• USB Port
• Navigation system: UVO eServices
• 8 Speakers
• Automatic temperature control
• Power driver seat with memory
• Leather-wrapped steering wheel
• Apple CarPlay & Android Auto

The Carnival's powerful V6 engine and 8-speed automatic transmission deliver an impressive blend of performance and efficiency, with a city fuel economy of 19 MPG and a highway rating of 26 MPG. Its roomy and versatile cabin offers seating for up to 8 passengers, ensuring everyone travels in comfort.

Experience the convenience of the Power Liftgate, which provides effortless access to the generous cargo area. The Carnival's advanced safety features, including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Electronic Stability Control, and Brake Assist, provide added peace of mind on the road.

description: Get ready to hit the road in style and comfort with this sleek silver 2012 Toyota Sienna! This versatile minivan is perfect for families on the go, with plenty of space for everyone and all their gear. Plus, you can rest easy knowing that this Sienna is equipped with top-notch safety features like child safety door locks, ABS brakes, and multiple airbags.Step inside and you'll find yourself surrounded by luxury and convenience. The leather seats are not only plush and comfortable but also easy to clean - perfect for those inevitable spills and messes. With separate climate controls for the driver and front passenger, everyone can ride in total comfort no matter the weather outside. Whether you're cruising down the highway or navigating busy city streets, you'll appreciate features like cruise control and steering wheel-mounted controls that make driving a breeze. The powerful yet efficient engine provides plenty of get-up-and-go while keeping fuel costs down. And with the electronic parking aid and keyless entry, parking and locking up at the end of the day is a snap.But the fun doesn't stop there - this Sienna is also loaded with creature comforts like an AM/FM radio, CD player, and a trip computer to keep you entertained on long drives. The power sunroof lets in plenty of natural light, while the automatic headlights and rear spoiler add a touch of sporty flair to this family-friendly ride.Safety is always a top priority, which is why this Sienna comes with a Carfax report available for your peace of mind. With features like traction control, vehicle stability control, and electronic brake assistance, you can drive with confidence knowing that you and your passengers are well protected.So why wait? Come test drive this 2012 Toyota Sienna today and see for yourself why it's the perfect blend of safety, style, and functionality for your family's next adventure. ****All of our retail units have been inspected and serviced by a 3rd party, ASE Certified shop. Please ask the dealer for the inspection. We spend countless hours purchasing the best possible vehicle's and list them at affordable prices. All prices are subject to a documention fee and applicable sales tax. For more information of this vehicle call us at 260-918-3030. description: 2020 Chrysler Pacifica Hybrid Limited Plug-In Hybrid | Panoramic Sunroof | Theater Package | Fully Loaded The 2020 Chrysler Pacifica Hybrid Limited is a premium plug-in hybrid minivan designed for families who want luxury, efficiency, and advanced technology. Its powered by a 3.6L V6 Hybrid engine paired with an EFlite Si-EVT transmission , delivering smooth performance with the ability to drive on electric power for short trips. This model offers an all-electric driving range of up to 32 miles and an EPA-estimated 82 MPGe combined , or 30 MPG combined on gasoline only . Finished in Granite Crystal Metallic Clear-Coat with a Black Nappa leather interior , this Limited trim offers a high-end cabin with seating comfort and premium materials throughout. Features include heated and ventilated front seats , heated steering wheel , driver memory , power front seats , Easy Slide second-row bucket seats , Stow n Go third-row seating , tri-zone automatic climate control , power sliding doors , and a hands-free power liftgate . Technology is a standout, highlighted by Uconnect 4 NAV with an 8.4-inch touchscreen , Apple CarPlay , Android Auto , Bluetooth , 4G LTE Wi-Fi hotspot , and a 13-speaker Alpine audio system . This Pacifica is equipped with Uconnect Theater , including rear seat video screens , Blu-Ray/DVD player , HDMI/USB media hubs , and wireless headphones , making it ideal for long trips. A tri-pane panoramic sunroof adds natural light and an open feel to all three rows. Safety is comprehensive with advanced driver-assistance features, including Blind Spot Monitoring , Rear Cross Path Detection , ParkSense front and rear park assist , 360-degree Surround View Camera , Adaptive Cruise Control with Stop & Go , Lane Departure Warning Plus , Forward Collision Warning with Active Braking , Automatic High Beams , and rain-sensing wipers . Key Features: 3.6L V6 Plug-In Hybrid Powertrain EFlite Si-EVT Automatic Transmission Up to 32-Mile All-Electric Range 82 MPGe Combined / 30 MPG Gasoline Only Nappa Leather Interior Heated & Ventilated Front Seats Tri-Pane Panoramic Sunroof Uconnect 4 NAV (8.4 Touchscreen) Apple CarPlay & Android Auto Uconnect Theater w/ Rear Video Screens 360 Camera & Advanced SafetyTec Group 13-Speaker Alpine Premium Audio See this 2020 Chrysler Pacifica Hybrid Limited today at Star Auto Sales in Meriden, CT . Financing and trade-in options are available for all credit types.

description:
Discover the versatile and efficient 2018 Ram ProMaster City Tradesman Cargo Van, a hardworking companion that's ready to take on your toughest tasks. With its spacious interior, impressive fuel economy, and array of convenient features, this van is the ideal solution for your business or personal needs.

• CARFAX Certified - No Accidents!
• ParkSense Rear Park Assist System
• Speed Control
• Daytime Running Headlamps

Powered by a 2.4L I4 MultiAir engine and paired with a 9-Speed 948TE Automatic transmission, this ProMaster City delivers an exceptional balance of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 21 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway. Its front-wheel-drive configuration provides confident handling and maneuverability, making it a breeze to navigate tight urban spaces or conquer long-haul deliveries.

The Quick Order Package 24C Tradesman Cargo Van equips this ProMaster City with a wealth of practical features, including Integrated Voice Command with Bluetooth, a 5-inch Uconnect touchscreen display, power windows, and remote keyless entry. The rear ParkSense Assist System and exterior backup camera make parking and maneuvering a seamless experience, while the durable cloth low-back bucket seats and cargo tie-down loops ensure your cargo stays secure.

Versatility is at the heart of the ProMaster City, with its sliding doors, rear cargo doors, and spacious interior offering ample room for your business needs or personal adventures. Whether you're transporting equipment, hauling supplies, or embarking on a cross-country journey, this van is up for the challenge.

Backed by a CARFAX Certified vehicle history and a comprehensive 180-point inspection, this 2018 Ram ProMaster City Tradesman Cargo Van is ready to take on your toughest jobs. Experience the confidence and capability that this van provides, and let it become the reliable workhorse you've been searching for.

180 Multi-Point Inspected, Serviced, and Fully Detailed. This vehicle is ready for immediate delivery, we offer nationwide shipping. Remember, at MTH of Forest Lake we take any and ALL trade-ins! Call now to schedule your appointment. All vehicle purchases are guaranteed 1 key. description:
Elevate your family's journeys with the exceptional 2018 Honda Odyssey EX-L. This well-appointed minivan offers unparalleled versatility, advanced technology, and a refined driving experience that will captivate you.

• New Tires
• Local Trade-In

The 2018 Odyssey EX-L is equipped with a powerful 3.5L V6 engine mated to a smooth-shifting 9-speed automatic transmission, delivering an impressive 19 city/28 highway MPG. Enjoy the confidence of front-wheel drive and the stability of Honda's renowned engineering.

Slip into the luxurious leather-trimmed interior and experience the convenience of the power driver's seat, heated front seats, and power moonroof. Stay connected with the 160-watt audio system, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto integration. The Blind Spot Information (BSI) System and Rear Camera provide added peace of mind on the road.

Versatility is at the heart of the Odyssey. The split-folding third-row seat and power liftgate make loading and unloading a breeze. With seating for up to eight passengers, this Honda offers ample room for your growing family and all their belongings.

Safety is paramount in the Odyssey, with features like advanced airbags, anti-lock brakes, and Honda Sensing® technologies to help you navigate the unexpected with confidence. The Odyssey's sleek exterior design and 18-inch alloy wheels exude a sophisticated presence on the road.

This 2018 Honda Odyssey EX-L is an exceptional value, combining premium features, exceptional utility, and Honda's renowned reliability. Experience the difference for yourself - schedule a test drive today and discover the joy of driving the Odyssey.

description:
STOW N GO • ONLY 84K MILES • V6 POWER • BLACKTOP PACKAGE • POWER LIFTGATE • BACKUP CAMERA • CLEAN CARFAX

2018 Dodge Grand Caravan SXT Billet Silver Metallic Clearcoat

If youre looking for maximum space, flexibility, and proven practicality, this 2018 Dodge Grand Caravan SXT delivers in all the right ways. With only 84,776 miles, a Clean CARFAX, and a recently serviced transmission, this well-maintained minivan is ready to handle everything from busy family schedules to road trips and daily commuting all while offering exceptional value.

Powered by Dodges dependable 3.6L V6 VVT engine paired with a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission, the Grand Caravan provides confident acceleration and effortless highway cruising. Front-wheel drive and a touring suspension help keep the ride comfortable and composed, whether youre navigating city streets or loading up for a weekend getaway.

What truly sets this Grand Caravan apart is its legendary Stow n Go seating. Both the second-row bucket seats and third-row split-bench fold flat into the floor, instantly transforming the cabin from people mover to cargo hauler no heavy seat removal required. Its one of the most versatile interiors ever offered in a minivan, perfect for families, contractors, or anyone who values flexibility.

Inside, this SXT trim feels upscale and thoughtfully designed. Premium seats with suede inserts, leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob, and silver accent stitching elevate the cabin, while dual-zone automatic climate control and rear air conditioning keep everyone comfortable. The Blacktop Package adds gloss black exterior accents, black headlamp bezels, and matching 17-inch aluminum wheels, giving this minivan a sportier, more modern look.

Technology and convenience features are plentiful. Youll enjoy a 6.5-inch touchscreen display, Bluetooth streaming audio, Uconnect voice command, steering wheel mounted controls, and SiriusXM capability. A ParkView rear backup camera, remote start, power liftgate, remote keyless entry, and power-adjustable drivers seat with lumbar support make daily driving easier and more enjoyable.

Safety is well covered with four-wheel disc brakes, electronic stability control, traction control, brake assist, advanced airbag coverage, and anti-whiplash head restraints. This Grand Caravan also earned recognition in the JD Power Initial Quality Study, reinforcing its reputation for reliability and owner satisfaction.

At Carter Subaru Ballard, we take pride in offering vehicles that meet our high standards for quality and value. Our team is here to provide a transparent, low-pressure experience and help you find the right fit for your lifestyle.

Spacious, versatile, and ready to work for you, this 2018 Dodge Grand Caravan SXT wont last long especially with miles this low. Stop by today to see it in person and take it for a test drive.

Carter Subaru Ballard
(206) 782-7475
www.cartersubaruballard.com

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

Discover the perfect blend of power, capability, and style with this 2022 Ford Ranger Lariat. This exceptional midsize truck is packed with premium features that elevate your driving experience to new heights.

• Hard Folding Tonneau Box Cover
• FX4 Off-Road Package with Terrain Management System, Trail Control, and Off-Road Tuned Suspension
• Trailer Tow Package with Class IV Hitch Receiver
• Technology Package with Navigation, Adaptive Cruise Control, and Forward Sensing System
• Premium B&O Sound System by Bang & Olufsen

Beneath the bold, Black exterior lies the impressive EcoBoost 2.3L I4 engine, delivering exceptional power and efficiency. With 4WD and the advanced Terrain Management System, you'll conquer any terrain with confidence, whether you're tackling the great outdoors or navigating the city streets.

The Ranger Lariat's interior is a sanctuary of comfort and convenience, featuring leather-trimmed heated front seats, dual-zone automatic climate control, and the cutting-edge SYNC 3 infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. Stay connected and in control, even on your longest adventures.

Safety is paramount, and this Ranger Lariat is equipped with a host of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Adaptive Cruise Control, Forward Sensing System, and a Rear Parking Camera, ensuring you and your loved ones arrive at your destination safely.

With its exceptional capability, premium features, and striking good looks, this 2022 Ford Ranger Lariat is the ultimate midsize truck for those who demand the best. Experience the difference for yourself – schedule a test drive today and discover the power and versatility that will elevate your driving experience.

description:
This BLIZZARD PEARL 2015 Toyota Sienna Ltd Premium with 209,741 miles has the style and comfort to fit your lifestyle! No Accidents! This vehicle is equipped with: Special Paint ($395 value)
    Limited Premium Package
    • Air Bag Beacon Mayday System
    • Daytime Running Lamp System
    • HID Headlamps
    • Electrochromic Mirror with Compass and Homelink
    • 4-Corner/back Clearance and Back Sonar
    • Front Tilt and Slide/rear Slide Sun Roof and Moon Roof
    • 60/40 Power Fold Rear Bench Seat
    • Large Screen 9x2 (Blu-Ray) Television and VTR
    • Rain Sensing Windshield Wipers
    Comfort
    • The steering wheel rim is heated.
    Convenience
    • Cruise control maintains a preset vehicle speed, automatically increasing or decreasing throttle to maintain that speed.
    • Access to the cargo area is gained via a large, power-operated rear door that opens upwards. This door may also contain the rear windshield of the vehicle.
    Safety and Security
    • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
    • Brake assist senses panic braking from the speed of the brake pedal's travel and applies all available power brake boost.
    Convenience
    • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
    • Power open and close liftgate - On-demand access. When your arms are full of cargo, the last thing you want to do is set it all down just to open the liftgate, then pick it all back up to load it in. By remotely opening and closing, power liftgate lets you skip straight to the loading. It also eliminates the awkward stretch to reach up for the liftgate to close it. Load and go with power open and close liftgate.
    In-car Entertainment
    • Entertainment system with Blu-ray - Keep boredom at bay. Whether it's driving cross- country or making a quick trip around town, your passengers' favorite videos can come, too! The Entertainment system with Blu-ray allows you to keep your crew entertained no matter where your journey takes you.
    Safety and Security
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
    It also has: Come in to see us today at 3905 Gerstner Memorial Dr Lake Charles LA 70607 or call (337) 426-1691 to schedule an appointment.

Let me show you what makes the 2024 Lexus UX 250h F SPORT Design such a smart and stylish choice.

Right away, you'll notice the F SPORT Design styling, the aggressive grille, bold black accents, and athletic wheels really give this SUV a standout look. Its compact and easy to maneuver, but it still has the presence of a true luxury vehicle.

Once you step inside, everything feels modern, premium, and driver, focused. The sport, inspired seats keep you comfortable and supported, the materials feel high end, and the layout is clean and easy to use. Lexus does an excellent job of making the interior feel upscale without being overwhelming.

Under the hood, this is where the UX really shines. Its a self charging hybrid, so you get excellent fuel efficiency without ever plugging it in. Its smooth, quiet, and responsive, perfect for daily commuting, city driving, or longer trips where comfort really matters.

Technology is front and center with a large touchscreen, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and an intuitive interface that makes everything feel effortless. And of course, Lexus Safety System+ is standard, giving you features like adaptive cruise control, lane keeping assist, and pre collision braking, all working in the background to keep you confident on the road.

What makes this UX special is how it blends everything together. You get sporty design, luxury comfort, advanced safety, and outstanding efficiency in one package. Its ideal for someone who wants something refined and smart, but still fun and stylish to drive.

If you're looking for a luxury SUV that looks great, saves you money on fuel, and still feels premium every time you get behind the wheel, the UX 250h F SPORT Design really checks all the boxes.

description: Carpeted Floormats, Gray, Leather-Trimmed Seats, Snow White Pearl. 2019 Kia Sedona EX Minivan 4D Overview The 2019 Kia Sedona EX Minivan is the sweet spot in the Sedona lineup, offering significant luxury and convenience features above the base trims without the price tag of the top-end SXL. The 2019 model year was notable as it introduced a major powertrain upgrade and minor styling refresh, making it a highly competitive choice in the segment. Performance and Drivetrain The 2019 Sedona delivered confident power, making highway merging and hauling a full load feel manageable. Engine: 3.3-liter V6 Gasoline Direct Injection (GDI) engine. Horsepower: 276 hp @ 6,000 rpm Torque: 248 lb-ft @ 5,200 rpm Transmission: A major upgrade for 2019 was the replacement of the old 6-speed automatic with a new, smoother, and more efficient 8-speed automatic transmission. Drivetrain: Standard Front-Wheel Drive (FWD). The combination of the powerful V6 and the efficient 8-speed transmission resulted in a smooth, quiet, and capable driving experience that often felt more like an SUV than a traditional minivan. The EX Trim: Key Features and Upgrades The EX trim elevates the Sedona from a basic people-mover to a genuinely comfortable family hauler by adding several crucial convenience and premium features: Exterior: The EX trim includes Power Sliding Side Doors, which are essential for minivan convenience, and power-folding exterior mirrors. It also features 18-inch alloy wheels and front fog lights. Interior Comfort: Upgrades include leather seat trim (replacing cloth), heated front seats, an auto-dimming rearview mirror, and a push-button start with a smart key. Climate Control: The EX features Tri-Zone Automatic Climate Control, allowing the driver, front passenger, and rear passengers to set their own preferred temperatures. Technology: It includes a UV-reducing solar control glass and a standard 7-inch touchscreen infotainment system with support for Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. Interior Utility and Passenger Comfort Minivans are judged on practicality, and the Sedona offers a smart solution for cargo management. Seating Configuration: The EX model typically seats 8 passengers (2 front, 3 in the second row, 3 in the third row). An optional 7-passenger configuration with premium second-row Captain?s Chairs was also available. Slide-N-Stow: This unique feature allows the second-row seats to slide forward and up against the front seats, offering substantial cargo space without requiring the heavy seats to be physically removed from the vehicle. Cargo Volume: Behind the third row, the Sedona offers about 33.9 cubic feet of cargo room. With the third row stowed into the floor and the second row collapsed via Slide-N-Stow, the total cargo capacity expands to over 142 cubic feet. Design: The Sedona?s dashboard and cockpit were intentionally designed to feel more like an SUV than a typical van, with a high center console and clean, modern lines. Safety and Driver Assistance The 2019 Sedona EX came standard with a rearview camera and rear parking sensors. Additional safety features often included in packages were: Blind Spot Collision Warning (BCW) Rear Cross-Traffic Collision Warning (RCCW) Parking Distance Warning (PDW) www.ellectramotors.com @Ellectra_Motors Ellectra Motors 6600 Jurupa Ave, Ste 215D Riverside, CA 92504 Tel & Text: 951.900.1614 . description:
Discover the perfect family companion in this 2016 Dodge Grand Caravan SE Plus. With its impressive features and versatile design, this minivan is the ideal choice for your daily adventures and weekend getaways.

Boasting an impressive array of amenities, this Grand Caravan SE Plus is equipped to elevate your driving experience:

• 100K WARRANTY AVAILABLE
• 3RD ROW SEATING
• 8 PASSENGER SEATING
• BLUETOOTH
• POWER WINDOWS, POWER LOCKS, TILT WHEEL, CRUISE CONTROL
• TILT AND TELESCOPIC STEERING WHEEL

The Quick Order Package 29Q SE Plus further enhances this vehicle, offering a range of premium features:

• 2nd Row Power Windows
• Power Quarter Vented Windows
• Body Color Bodyside Molding
• Premium Interior Accents
• Body Color Sill Applique
• Rear Air Conditioning with Heater
• SIRIUS Satellite Radio
• Bluetooth Streaming Audio
• Leather Wrapped Steering Wheel and Shift Knob
• Rear View Auto Dim Mirror with Microphone
• 2 Row Stow 'N Go with Tailgate Seats
• Front & Rear Power Windows with Front 1-Touch
• 3 Zone Manual Control Front & Rear A/C

Powered by a robust 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine and equipped with a 6-Speed Automatic transmission, this Grand Caravan delivers a confident and efficient performance, achieving an impressive 17 MPG in the city and 25 MPG on the highway.

Beyond its impressive capabilities, this Grand Caravan SE Plus also boasts a sleek gray exterior, complemented by a well-appointed interior that seamlessly blends style and functionality. With its spacious and versatile cabin, you'll have ample room to accommodate your family and all their belongings, whether it's a weekend getaway or a daily commute.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like Anti-Lock Brakes, Electronic Stability Control, and a comprehensive airbag system providing you and your loved ones with the protection you deserve.

If you're in the market for a reliable, feature-rich, and family-friendly minivan, this 2016 Dodge Grand Caravan SE Plus is an exceptional choice. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by its exceptional value and the exceptional ownership experience it can provide.

Provided the vehicle passes inspection, vehicles will be eligible for the 6 month/6,000 mile limited warranty. description: Discover the fantastic blend of space, comfort, and reliability that the 2016 Honda Odyssey EX-L brings to your lifestyle. This remarkable minivan, with a clean title and sleek design, showcases an impressive 131,603 miles on the odometer—a remarkably low average of almost 21,934 miles per year, which is gently above the national average for vehicles this age. Whether it's daily commutes, weekend getaways, or the all-important family road trip, the Odyssey is engineered to enhance your driving experience. With Honda’s reputation for durability and sophistication, you can rest assured that this vehicle is ready for what life throws at you.. Beneath the hood, you'll find a robust 3.5L V6 SOHC 24-Valve i-VTEC engine, delivering 248 horsepower and 250 lb-ft of torque that propels you with confidence while maintaining impressive fuel efficiency. The Odyssey offers 19 MPG in the city and an astonishing 28 MPG on the highway, ensuring that your wallet remains happy even on long excursions. The powerful automatic transmission complements the engine’s capabilities, providing smooth and effortless shifts, whether you're cruising through city streets or tackling the open road.. Experience a driving dynamic that prioritizes both performance and safety. The Front Wheel Drive (FWD) system enhances handling and maneuverability, ideal for tackling varying driving conditions while providing a comfortable ride. The Odyssey is also equipped with a suite of safety features, including ABS brakes, brake assist, and stability control. And let's not forget the back-up camera which makes parking and reversing easier than ever, providing an extra layer of confidence whether you’re in the grocery store lot or lining up at the park.... Read the full description on our Website at: www.shawsautosales.com

With 143K miles and a 1-owner history, this Sienna has been regularly serviced in Arkansas and is ready for its next chapter. Offered by Evoke Autos, your trusted used car dealer in Jonesboro serving Northeast Arkansas.The LE trim blends value and practicality, featuring a full 8-passenger seating configuration, power sliding side doors, and Toyota s Entune touchscreen system with Bluetooth and backup camera. Recent services include oil change, air filters, tire work, and alignment this van is road-trip ready.? Key Standard Features:
  • 3.5L V6 engine (296 hp)
  • 8-passenger seating w/second-row bench
  • Tri-zone automatic climate control
  • Power sliding doors (dual)
  • Entune Audio Plus w/7 touchscreen
  • Bluetooth + Backup camera
  • Cruise control + steering wheel audio controls
  • Roof rails + privacy glass
  • USB/AUX input + 6-speaker audio
  • Power driver seat
  • Split & stow 3rd-row seat
??? Recent service: oil/filter, alignment, air filter, tiresEvoke Autos is located at 5800 E Highland Dr in Jonesboro, Arkansas just one hour from Memphis, TN. Every vehicle in our inventory is thoroughly inspected and serviced, which allows us to offer extended warranty options for added peace of mind. All vehicles are Carfax Certified with a clean title, and the current Carfax report is available to view directly on our website just click the Carfax logo next to the listing.We offer flexible financing options through a wide range of lenders, including local banks and credit unions, and we work with customers from out of state as well. Trade-ins are always welcome, even if you still owe money on your current vehicle.Have questions? Call or text us anytime at 870-604-4114 we're here to help.

Discover the exceptional 2023 Kia Sportage X-Pro, a versatile and well-equipped SUV that's ready to elevate your driving experience. With its sleek black exterior, this Sportage boasts a commanding presence on the road, complemented by a spacious and well-appointed interior.

• CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED PLUS COMES WITH 7 YEARS OR 100,000 MILES LIMITED WARRANTY (Optional Warranty)
• CERTIFIED BY CARFAX - NO ACCIDENTS!
• CERTIFIED BY CARFAX - ONE OWNER!
• REAR VIEW BACK-UP CAMERA!
• BLUETOOTH HANDS-FREE CALLING!
• HEATED SEATS!
• LEATHER SEATS!
• NON SMOKER!
• PANORAMIC MOONROOF!

Under the hood, the Sportage X-Pro is powered by a robust I4 engine paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission and all-wheel drive, delivering an impressive blend of performance and efficiency with 23 city/28 highway MPG.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a wealth of premium features that cater to your every need. The Sportage X-Pro boasts a state-of-the-art infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, allowing you to seamlessly integrate your smartphone. The panoramic moonroof floods the cabin with natural light, creating a bright and airy atmosphere, while the heated leather seats ensure your comfort on even the coldest days.

Safety is a top priority in the Sportage X-Pro, with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies that include automatic emergency braking, lane-keep assist, and a rearview camera. You can navigate with confidence, knowing that your Sportage is equipped to keep you and your loved ones secure.

Whether you're embarking on a family road trip or tackling your daily commute, the 2023 Kia Sportage X-Pro is the perfect companion. With its exceptional features, versatile capabilities, and striking good looks, this SUV is sure to exceed your expectations.

Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive at our dealership today. We're confident that once you get behind the wheel, you'll be captivated by the Sportage X-Pro's remarkable blend of style, performance, and practicality.

description:
This 2014 Honda Odyssey EX-L, has a Dark Cherry Pearl exterior and an Beige interior color. 88,191 miles. Stock Number 4433. One Owner! OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Comfort
  • Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions - That's hot. Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions provide more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower body pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in heated driver and front passenger seat cushions.
Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
  • Power open and close liftgate - On-demand access. When your arms are full of cargo, the last thing you want to do is set it all down just to open the liftgate, then pick it all back up to load it in. By remotely opening and closing, power liftgate lets you skip straight to the loading. It also eliminates the awkward stretch to reach up for the liftgate to close it. Load and go with power open and close liftgate.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Voice activated integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, the voice activated integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. Just tell it where you want to go, and the voice activated integrated navigation system shows you the right way.

Discover the exceptional value and uncompromising quality of this 2022 Toyota Corolla LE. With its sleek exterior, spacious interior, and impressive array of features, this sedan is the perfect blend of style, comfort, and practicality.

Elevate your driving experience with standout features such as a Backup Camera, Bluetooth connectivity, Cruise Control, and Lane Departure Warning. Additionally, this Corolla LE boasts:

• Back-up Cam
• Bluetooth
• Cruise Control
• FWD
• Lane Departure Warning

Designed with your safety in mind, this Corolla LE is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety technologies, including ABS brakes, Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Electronic Stability Control, and a Rear-View Camera. You can drive with confidence, knowing you and your loved ones are well-protected.

The efficient 1.8L I4 DOHC 16V engine, paired with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission and Front-Wheel Drive, delivers an exceptional balance of power and fuel economy. With an EPA-estimated 30 MPG in the city and 38 MPG on the highway, you'll enjoy exceptional value at the pump.

Step inside this well-appointed Corolla LE and experience the comfort and convenience of features like Automatic Temperature Control, Power Windows, Remote Keyless Entry, and Steering Wheel-Mounted Audio Controls. The premium fabric seat trim and split-folding rear seat provide both style and versatility, ensuring a comfortable and customizable driving experience.

Connectivity is key in today's world, and this Corolla LE delivers with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, allowing you to seamlessly integrate your smartphone and access your favorite apps, music, and navigation with ease.

Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and efficiency in this 2022 Toyota Corolla LE. Experience the confidence and peace of mind that comes with owning a reliable and well-equipped Toyota. Visit our showroom today to take this exceptional vehicle for a test drive and see how it can elevate your driving experience.

Boasting an impressive array of enhancements, this Elantra SEL is equipped with:

• Wireless Device Charging

• Power Sunroof

The Elantra's 2.0L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine, paired with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission, delivers an exceptional balance of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 31 MPG in the city and an impressive 41 MPG on the highway. Beyond its impressive performance, this Elantra SEL is packed with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including Forward Collision Avoidance Assist, Pedestrian and Cyclist Detection, and a Rear Parking Camera. These cutting-edge technologies work seamlessly to help keep you and your loved ones secure on the road.

As a Hyundai Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, this Elantra SEL has undergone a rigorous 173-point inspection and is backed by a comprehensive warranty. You can drive with confidence, knowing that your investment is protected by Hyundai's industry-leading coverage, including a 60-month/60,000-mile limited warranty and a 120-month/100,000-mile powertrain warranty.

Experience the exceptional quality, advanced technology, and unparalleled value that this 2022 Hyundai Elantra SEL has to offer. Schedule a test drive today and discover how this meticulously maintained sedan can elevate your driving experience.

This 2021 Volkswagen Tiguan 2.0T SE is a remarkable SUV that combines style, capability, and convenience. With its sleek gray exterior and spacious interior, this Tiguan is ready to take on your daily adventures and weekend getaways.

Powered by a 2.0L TSI DOHC engine and equipped with an 8-Speed Automatic with Tiptronic transmission, this Tiguan delivers a smooth and responsive driving experience. The all-wheel-drive system ensures confident handling in a variety of road conditions, while the fuel-efficient 21 city/27 highway MPG ratings make it an economical choice.

Step inside and discover the Tiguan's impressive array of features. The panoramic sunroof fills the cabin with natural light, creating an open and airy atmosphere. The frameless auto-dimming rearview mirror enhances your visibility and convenience, while the 2-row rubber monster mats and heavy-duty trunk liner protect your vehicle's interior from wear and tear.

For added peace of mind, this Tiguan comes with the VW CARE prepaid scheduled maintenance contract, ensuring your SUV receives the care it deserves. The Combination Assistance Kit provides essential emergency supplies, making it a valuable companion on the road.

Packed with amenities like heated front seats, a power driver's seat, and a host of advanced safety features, this 2021 Volkswagen Tiguan 2.0T SE is the perfect blend of style, comfort, and capability. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today.

Choose Westgate Chrysler Jeep Dodge Ram in Raleigh, NC for a dealership experience built on transparency, value, and customer-first service. With a wide selection of new CJDR models and an extensive inventory of quality used cars, trucks, and SUVs, Westgate is a trusted destination for shoppers across Raleigh, Durham, the Triangle and all of North Carolina.

description:
This 2022 Ford F-550 Super Duty XL DRW in Oxford White is a heavy-duty powerhouse built for maximum performance and reliability. Equipped with a Power Stroke 6.7L V8 Turbodiesel engine and 4WD, this truck is a CARFAX One-Owner with a Clean CARFAX and a recent arrival. Ford Gold Certified for added peace of mind, it features the GVWR 19,500 lb Payload Plus Upgrade Package, dual rear wheels, limited-slip rear axle with 4.88 ratio, and 332-amp alternators, making it ready for demanding work environments. With the Dump Body, Utility Lighting System, and Snow Plow Prep Package, this F-550 is fully equipped to handle any commercial or heavy-duty task.

Inside, the cabin balances functionality with comfort and convenience, featuring HD vinyl 40/20/40 split bench seating, front center armrest with storage, power locks and windows, and steering wheel-mounted audio controls. Additional features include folding trailer tow mirrors with power-heated glass, remote keyless entry, trailer brake controller, and transmission power take-off provision for specialized equipment. Available now at AutoFair Ford of Manchester, New Hampshirethe #1 Ford Certified and #1 Used Ford Dealer in New England, proudly serving Manchester, Concord, Nashua, Salem, Londonderry, Laconia, Rochester, and Exeter. See more at https://www.autofairford.com/

Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Keyfob engine start control - Get an early start. Remotely start your vehicle's engine from the key fob, ensuring your ride is ready to go when you get in. Now you can stay comfortable inside while your vehicle gets comfortable outside, thanks to Keyfob engine start control.Safety and Security Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedals travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.Technology and Telematics Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road. Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicles private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot. Come on in to Twin City Buick GMC today at 3046 Airport Highway Alcoa TN 37701 or call to schedule a test drive!

description:
Discover the versatility and capability of the 2023 Ford Transit-350 Base, a hardworking commercial vehicle tailored to meet the demands of your business. This rugged and efficient van is the perfect companion for your delivery, transportation, or service needs.

Boasting a MORGAN 14' BOX TRUCK, this Transit-350 is equipped with a powerful 3.5L V6 Twin Turbocharged (EcoBoost) engine, delivering exceptional performance and fuel efficiency. Complementing this impressive powertrain is a 10-Speed Automatic transmission with Overdrive and a 3.73 Limited-Slip Axle Ratio, ensuring smooth and responsive handling, even when fully loaded.

Key features of this Transit-350 Base include:
• 3.5L V6 Twin Turbocharged (EcoBoost) engine with Auto Start-Stop Technology
• Interior Upgrade Package with Dark Palazzo Gray Cloth Bucket Seats and illuminated features
• Long-Arm Manual-Folding Heated Power Adjust Mirrors with turn signals
• Cruise Control with Adjustable Speed Limiting Device
• Dual AGM Batteries (70 Amp-Hr Each)
• AM/FM Stereo with SYNC 3, Bluetooth, and Rear Video Camera Prep Kit
• Back-Up Alarm, Front Fog Lamps, and Daytime Running Lights

Designed with your business in mind, the 2023 Ford Transit-350 Base offers a versatile and capable platform to tackle a wide range of commercial tasks. The spacious cargo area, combined with a robust powertrain and advanced features, make this van an exceptional choice for your transportation needs.

Experience the confidence and efficiency of the 2023 Ford Transit-350 Base. Visit our showroom today and let our knowledgeable sales team demonstrate how this hardworking van can transform your business operations.

Vehicle Details
2023 Chevrolet Silverado 2500 Work Truck 4WD — powerful capability, rugged reliability, and unbeatable value in Roanoke, VA. This V8 6.6L gasoline-powered heavy-duty pickup delivers the towing strength and torque you need for demanding jobs, while providing modern tech and comfort features for every drive. With Hands Free Bluetooth and Apple CarPlay, stay connected and in control whether you're heading to a job site or running errands around town. XM Radio keeps the ride entertaining, and the Back-Up Camera makes hitching trailers and backing into tight spots safer and simpler. This Chevrolet Silverado is a CARFAX 1-Owner vehicle, showing careful use and full-service history for added peace of mind. The Work Truck trim focuses on durability and function — heavy-duty suspension, a capable 4WD system, and a bed built to handle gear, tools, and supplies. If you're searching for dependable towing and hauling with modern connectivity, this truck blends classic V8 performance with practical technology. Located in Roanoke, VA, this 2023 Chevrolet Silverado 2500 Work Truck is priced to move — offering the best price locally for comparable condition and features. Whether you need a reliable fleet truck or a weekend warrior with serious capability, this Chevy delivers. Contact us to schedule a test drive in Roanoke and see why this 2500 Work Truck is the smart choice for performance, value, and dependability.

Equipment
This vehicle is equipped with the latest generation of XM/Sirius Radio. This vehicle is a certified CARFAX 1-owner. Apple CarPlay: Seamless smartphone integration for this Chevrolet Silverado - stay connected and entertained on the go! Bluetooth technology is built into it, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. See what's behind you with the back up camera on this Chevrolet Silverado. This Chevrolet Silverado comes equipped with Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration on the road. Keep safely connected while in this 3/4 ton pickup with OnStar. You may enjoy services like Automatic Crash Response, Navigation, Roadside Assistance and Hands-Free Calling. This Chevrolet Silverado embodies class and sophistication with its refined white exterior. When you encounter slick or muddy roads, you can engage the four wheel drive on this Chevrolet Silverado and drive with confidence. The Chevrolet Silverado has a V8, 6.6L high output engine.

Packages
WT Convenience Package: Remote Keyless Entry, EZ Lift Power Lock and Release Tailgate, Deep-Tinted Glass, Heated Vertical Trailering Mirrors, Electric Rear-Window Defogger, Electronic Cruise Control with Set and Resume Speed. Snow Plow Prep/camper Package: 220 Amp Alternator, Skid Plates. OnStar and Chevrolet Connected Services Capable. Spare LT265/70R17E AT BW Tire. Integrated Trailer Brake Controller. Electronic Cruise Control with Set and Resume Speed. Electric Rear-Window Defogger. 120-Volt Instrument Panel Power Outlet. LT265/70R17E AT BW Tires. Chrome Front Bumper. Deep-Tinted Glass. Skid Plates. SiriusXM Radio. SEO: Rear Camera Kit. SEO: Back-Up Alarm Calibration. **Equipment listed is based on original vehicle build and subject to change. description:
Discover the exceptional 2023 Ford Transit-350 Base, a versatile and reliable workhorse built to handle your toughest tasks. This impressive vehicle boasts a range of impressive features that make it the perfect choice for your business or personal transportation needs.

Highlighted Features:
• MORGAN 14' BOX TRUCK
• 3.5L V6 Twin Turbocharged (EcoBoost) with Auto Start-Stop Technology
• Interior Upgrade Package with Dark Palazzo Gray Cloth Bucket Seats
• Long-Arm Manual-Folding Heated Power Adjust Mirrors with Turn Signals
• Cruise Control with Adjustable Speed Limiting Device
• 3.73 Limited-Slip Axle Ratio
• Dual AGM Batteries (70 Amp-hr Each)
• Radio: AM/FM Stereo with SYNC 3, Bluetooth, and 4 Speakers
• Rear Video Camera & Prep Kit
• Back Up Alarm

This 2023 Ford Transit-350 Base is the epitome of versatility and capability. Equipped with the powerful EcoBoost V6 engine, this van delivers impressive performance and efficiency, making it the ideal choice for a wide range of applications. The Interior Upgrade Package adds a touch of sophistication, with premium cloth bucket seats and illuminated features that enhance the driving experience.

The long-arm manual-folding heated power adjust mirrors with turn signals provide excellent visibility and convenience, while the cruise control with adjustable speed limiting device ensures a smooth and controlled ride, even in heavy traffic. The 3.73 limited-slip axle ratio and dual AGM batteries provide the durability and reliability you need to tackle any job.

Step inside and enjoy the advanced technology, including the SYNC 3 infotainment system with Bluetooth connectivity and a rear video camera prep kit for enhanced safety and awareness. With the back-up alarm, you can navigate tight spaces with confidence, knowing your surroundings are well-monitored.

This 2023 Ford Transit-350 Base is a true workhorse, built to handle your toughest challenges with ease. Experience the power, versatility, and premium features that make this van an exceptional choice for your business or personal transportation needs. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover the remarkable capabilities of this remarkable vehicle.

description:
CARFAX 1-Owner, Cadillac Certified. Leather, Aluminum Wheels, Onboard Communications System, iPod/MP3 Input, Satellite Radio, Power Liftgate, Turbo Charged Engine, DRIVER AWARENESS PACKAGE, COLD WEATHER PACKAGE, SAFETY ALERT PACKAGE

SERVICE COMPLETED
Service Work completed on this Cadillac XT4 included: Complete Multi-Point Inspection, Oil & Filter Change by a Factory Trained Technician, Battery Voltage Test, Tires Inspected, Brake Inspection, Emissions System Check, Professional Detailed Inside and Out, Function Test all Lights, Check the Complete Exhaust System, Cooling System Inspection, Transmission Fluid Inspection, Differential Fluid Inspection, Function Test all Options & Accessories.

KEY FEATURES INCLUDE
Leather Seats, Power Liftgate, Satellite Radio, iPod/MP3 Input, Onboard Communications System. Cadillac FWD Premium Luxury with LATTE METALLIC exterior and LIGHT PLATINUM/JET BLACK interior features a 4 Cylinder Engine with 235 HP at 5000 RPM*.

OPTION PACKAGES
ENHANCED VISIBILITY PACKAGE includes (UKK) Rear Pedestrian Alert, (DRZ) Rear Camera Mirror, (CWA) Rear Camera Mirror Washer, (UV2) HD Surround Vision and (UKG) Automatic Parking Assist with braking, AUDIO SYSTEM, BOSE CENTERPOINT SURROUND SOUND 13-SPEAKER SYSTEM with auxiliary amplifier, COLD WEATHER PACKAGE includes (KA1) heated driver and front passenger seats, (KA6) heated rear outboard seating position seats and (KI3) heated steering wheel (Vehicles built prior to November 15, 2021 and after May 1, 2022, include driver and front passenger heated seats and heated rear outboard seats. Certain vehicles built on or after November 15, 2021 through May 1, 2022, will be forced to include (00V) Not Equipped with Driver and Front Passenger Heated Seats, which removes driver and front passenger heated seats and (00R) Not Equipped with Heated Rear Outboard Seats, which removes heated rear outboard seats. Vehicles built prior to December 6, 2021 and after May 1, 2022, include heated steering wheel. Certain vehicles built on or after December 6, 2021 through May 1, 2022, will be, DRIVER AWARENESS PACKAGE includes (UE4) Following Distance Indicator, (UHX) Lane Keep Assist with Lane Departure Warning and (TQ5) IntelliBeam, SAFETY ALERT PACKAGE includes (UKC) Lane Change Alert with Side Blind Zone Alert and (UFG) Rear Cross Traffic Alert, ENGINE, 2.0L TURBO, 4-CYLINDER, SIDI (235 hp [175 kW] @ 5000 rpm, 258 lb-ft of torque [350 N-m] @ 1500-4000 rpm) (STD), TRANSMISSION, 9-SPEED AUTOMATIC electronically-controlled (STD).

PRICED TO MOVE
Reduced from $30,995. This XT4 is priced $1,300 below J.D. Power Retail.

PURCHASE WITH CONFIDENCE
CARFAX 1-Owner 172-Point Vehicle Inspection, including road test performed by trained Cadillac technicians, 1 year-unlimited mile Limited Warranty upon expiration of the New Vehicle Limited Warranty, $0 Deductible, All scheduled maintenance performed and up to date, Can be serviced at any Cadillac dealer nationwide, 24-Hour Roadside Assistance with Courtesy Transportation, Satellite radio-equipped vehicles include a 3-month trial to SiriusXM All Access package

OUR OFFERINGS
Pine Belt Cadillac customers love the luxury and quality of a Cadillac, and with good reason. The Cadillac lineup is filled with personality, gusto and glamour. Celebrating over 100 years of luxurious automotive manufacturing, Cadillac gives tangible proof of its commitment to push the boundaries of design and engineering.

Don't settle for anything less than the best. This 2023 Ford F-350SD XL is the perfect blend of power, versatility, and sophistication. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this truck should be your next automotive investment.

This rugged 2023 Chevrolet Silverado 2500HD Work Truck in clean Summit White comes equipped with a practical service body bed, making it ready for immediate use by contractors, tradesmen, or fleet operators. With only 51183 miles, this low-mileage Double Cab features a powerful 6.6L V8 engine and smooth 6-Speed Automatic transmission in rear-wheel drive, plus the WT Convenience Package that includes remote keyless entry, deep-tinted glass, rear-window defogger, cruise control, heated and power-adjustable trailering mirrors, trailer brake controller, and OnStar services with Wi-Fi hotspot capability. The durable Jet Black cloth interior offers comfortable seating for the crew, while the installed service body provides secure storage, tool organization, and versatile workspace right out of the gate.

Built for tough jobs and heavy-duty performance, this 2023 Silverado 2500HD Work Truck combines Chevrolet's legendary strength with the added convenience of a pre-installed service body, all-season spare tire, and trailer-ready features for maximum productivity. An exceptional value for anyone needing a turn-key work truck that's already customized and in excellent condition. Visit Sierra Subaru of Monrovia today at www.sierrasubaru.com to see this capable rig in person, schedule a test drive, or get full details on VIN 1GB2WLE75PF173166 and Stock #DP73166. Your next work truck is waiting!

description:
Discover the power and versatility of the 2018 GMC Sierra 3500HD Base, a true workhorse that's ready to tackle any job. With its robust Vortec 6.0L V8 engine and 4WD capabilities, this truck is built to conquer the toughest terrain and handle the most demanding tasks.

• 4WD
• Back-up Cam
• Bluetooth
• Cruise Control
• Trailer Hitch
• 3 Pass
• Dump
• Dually
• Plow Pack.
• Power Windows
• Sierra Convenience Package
• Snow Plow Prep Package
• Trailer Brake Controller, Integrated
• Transfer Case, Electronic Shift with Rotary Dial Controls
• Tires, LT235/80R17E All-Terrain
• Power Outlet, 110-Volt AC

This Sierra 3500HD is equipped with a host of features that make it the ultimate work companion. The Sierra Convenience Package adds essential upgrades like heated power-adjustable mirrors, auto-dimming rearview mirror, and remote keyless entry. The Snow Plow Prep Package equips the truck with the power and protection needed for heavy-duty snow removal, including a 220-amp alternator, underbody shields, and provisions for a cab roof-mounted lamp.

Whether you're hauling heavy loads, towing a trailer, or plowing through snow, the Sierra 3500HD's impressive capabilities will make your job easier. The integrated trailer brake controller and 4.10 rear axle ratio ensure smooth and confident towing, while the durable dually configuration provides exceptional stability and load-carrying capacity.

But this truck isn't just about brute strength – it also offers impressive comfort and convenience features. The 7-inch color touchscreen infotainment system, Bluetooth connectivity, and premium audio system keep you connected and entertained on the job. The power windows, tilt-adjustable steering wheel, and available power-adjustable heated mirrors add to the truck's user-friendly design.

Experience the ultimate in heavy-duty performance and versatility with the 2018 GMC Sierra 3500HD Base. Discover how this rugged and well-equipped truck can transform the way you work. Visit our showroom today to take it for a test drive and see how it can meet your demanding needs.

The Fazza Price shown includes a $1,000 trade-in assistance credit when you trade in an eligible vehicle (10 years old or newer with under 120,000 miles) and be in proper running condition at the time of the sale. If you do not have a qualifying trade-in, the purchase price will increase by $1,000. Taxes, title, registration, and an $895 documentation fee are not included. Contact Fazza Motors for the latest pricing and availability.

description: This 2018 Ford Transit-350 in classic Oxford White is the ultimate partner for your business or specialized hauling needs. Built as a heavy-duty RWD workhorse, it features the robust 3.7L V6 Ti-VCT engine and a dual rear wheel (DRW) configuration. This "dually" setup provides enhanced stability and a higher payload capacity, making it ideal for those who need a reliable platform for a box truck, service body, or heavy delivery routes.The Exterior Upgrade Package ensures this Transit looks as professional as your business. It adds polished touches like a chrome grille and headlamp trim, elevating the vans appearance on the road. With the 4.10 axle ratio, this Ford is geared for low-end torque and towing, giving you the extra muscle needed to move heavy loads with ease and confidence.Inside, the cabin is focused on driver productivity and comfort. You'll find durable Pewter Vinyl dual bucket seats that are built to handle the rigors of daily commercial use. The interior is also equipped with modern essentials like Cruise Control, a message center to keep you updated on vehicle health, and a radio with Bluetooth connectivity so you can stay hands-free while navigating your workday.Safety is paramount in a large vehicle, and this Transit-350 is well-equipped to protect its occupants. It features a comprehensive airbag system, including thorax side airbags and the Safety Canopy side curtain system. With Electronic Stability Control and 4-wheel disc brakes, you have a stable and responsive ride even when the van is fully loaded. This vehicle also comes with a Clean CARFAX, ensuring you're getting a well-maintained tool for your trade.At the Superior Pre-Owned Superstore of Bentonville, we know that your vehicle is an investment in your success. This Ford Transit has been thoroughly cleaned and serviced to ensure its ready to hit the ground running from day one. Let us help you find the right vehicle at an unparalleled price. Visit us today and see how our straightforward, "extra-mile" service can help you grow your business!Faster. Simpler. More Transparent. Superior Automotive Group has helped thousands of customers find the right car by leveraging one of Arkansas' largest selections of new and pre-owned vehicles at unparalleled prices. Yet, it's our extra-mile customer service and uncommonly candid and respectful staff that have won the trust and loyalty of Arkansas drivers for 30 years. Come visit one of our Superior dealerships today and let us exceed your expectations.

description: Get the job done in style and comfort with this excellent-condition 2012 Chevrolet Express 2500 — a hardworking, dependable full-size van powered by a strong 6.0L FlexFuel V8 that delivers 323 hp and 373 lb-ft of torque. Cheerful, capable, and built for business or big-family duty, this Express is ready for the road or the worksite. What you’ll love - Potent FlexFuel V8: The 6.0L V8 gives you robust low-end torque for towing and hauling, and FlexFuel capability adds fuel flexibility. Smooth, dependable power makes city driving and highway cruising effortless. - Heavy-duty platform: Built on a rugged 2500-series chassis, this Express is engineered to carry payloads and handle towing chores with confidence. Suspension and brakes are tuned for commercial-duty use so you get durability mile after mile. Factory-installed features (detailed) - Powertrain and drivetrain: Factory-mounted 6.0L FlexFuel V8 paired with an automatic transmission and rear-wheel drive. The drivetrain is designed for durability and steady, predictable performance when loaded. - Exterior practicality: Classic, utilitarian van styling with large rear barn doors for easy loading and unloading, an available sliding side door for curbside access, and big exterior mirrors to improve visibility while maneuvering or towing. - Interior and cargo: A spacious cabin with a functional layout — generous cargo volume or passenger room depending on configuration. Factory materials focus on durability: heavy-duty seat coverings and floors designed to withstand daily use. Multiple tie-down points, flat load surfaces, and a wide rear opening make loading tools, gear, or cargo straightforward. - Comfort and convenience: Factory HVAC system with strong heating and cooling to keep the cabin comfortable in all seasons. Tilt steering wheel and cruise control help reduce driver fatigue on long runs. Practical storage cubbies and overhead console space keep paperwork and essentials organized. - Audio and connectivity: Factory AM/FM stereo with CD capability and auxiliary input for connecting mobile devices — simple, user-friendly entertainment and hands-on controls within easy reach. - Safety and control: Built-in safety equipment includes front airbags, anti-lock braking, and a chassis engineered for stability and control under load. Large mirrors and a commanding driving position improve overall awareness on the road. Condition This Express 2500 is in excellent overall condition — well-maintained, clean, and ready to work. Mechanically strong and visually tidy, it presents as a dependable solution whether you need a cargo hauler, work van, or fleet-ready vehicle. If you’re after a no-nonsense, powerful full-size van with proven durability and a flexible interior, this 2012 Chevrolet Express 2500 is a smart, cheerful choice! This one shows up in a crisp white exterior with a practical gray interior, is in excellent overall condition, has a clean CARFAX, and has had just one previous owner — the kind you actually want on the title. Factory features (aka the stuff Chevy thoughtfully installed before you decided to make it your daily hero): - Powertrain and driveline - Vortec 6.0L FlexFuel V8 — runs regular gas or E85, so you can be flexible about fuel like your schedule (360 hp / 380 lb-ft). - Smooth-shifting automatic transmission built to handle heavy-duty work without drama. - Heavy-duty 2500-series chassis and suspension designed for towing, hauling, and not backing down from a long day. - Bed and toolbox - Factory-installed tool box mounted in the bed — perfect for keeping wrenches, straps, and questionable lunch choices where they belong. - Durable pickup bed with a tailgate made to live a hard life and still look respectable on Mondays. - Exterior - Clean WHITE paint that hides a multitude of sins (and looks good on every jobsite and driveway). - Simple, functional exterior trim focused on utility — not frills, just performance. - Interior and comfort - Gray interior with durable materials chosen to survive boots, mud, and the occasional coffee mishap. - Practical seating and roomy layout that puts comfort within reach after a long drive or a longer job. - Large, easy-to-use controls and generous storage cubbies for work gloves, paperwork, and emergency snacks. - Convenience and utility - Factory-grade gauges and switches that are intuitive when your hands are full of tools. - Multiple 12V outlets for powering jobsite devices, phone chargers, and the always-important coffee warmer. - Simple audio system for radio, CDs, or your collection of playlists — made to play through your day without fuss. - Safety and durability - Built strong with heavy-duty brakes and stability-enhancing systems to keep you in control when the job gets interesting. - Front airbags and supplemental restraint systems installed to factory specifications for day-to-day peace of mind. - Robust construction and quality engineering designed for durability and long service life. ***918-921-2100*** Tough, Capable, and Built to Last - Introducing the 2015 Chevrolet Silverado 3500HD Work Truck

Seeking a workhorse that can handle your toughest jobs? Look no further than the 2015 Chevrolet Silverado 3500HD Work Truck. This rugged and reliable pickup is the perfect companion for your demanding lifestyle. With its impressive Duramax 6.6L V8 Turbodiesel engine and Allison 1000 6-Speed Automatic transmission, this Silverado is ready to take on any challenge you throw its way.

• ***918-921-2100***
• T-Town is Truck Town
• Never A Rental
• 6.6L V8 Diesel Turbocharged Duramax
• Allison 1000 6-Speed Automatic Transmission
• WT Convenience Package
• Trailer Brake Controller, Integrated
• Chevrolet MyLink Audio System with 4.2" Diagonal Color Screen
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Electronic Stability Control
• Exhaust Brake
• Power Take Off Engine Control Provisions
• Vertical Camper Heated Outside Mirrors
• Inside Rear-View Auto-Dimming Mirror

This Silverado is built to work hard and play hard. With its powerful Duramax engine and Allison transmission, you'll have the muscle to tow and haul with ease. The WT Convenience Package adds essential features like remote keyless entry, an auto-dimming rearview mirror, and heated, power-adjustable outside mirrors – making your driving experience more comfortable and convenient.

But this truck isn't just about brute strength. It's also equipped with the latest technology, including the Chevrolet MyLink infotainment system with a 4.2" color display, Bluetooth connectivity, and voice-activated controls. Stay connected and entertained on the go, all while keeping your hands on the wheel and your eyes on the road.

Reliability is key when it comes to a work truck, and the Silverado 3500HD delivers. With its robust construction and proven Duramax/Allison powertrain, you can count on this truck to tackle your toughest tasks day in and day out. And with the added convenience features, you'll be able to work harder and smarter, not just harder.

Don't settle for a truck that can't keep up with your demands. Upgrade to the 2015 Chevrolet Silverado 3500HD Work Truck and experience the power, capability, and technology that will make your job easier and more efficient. Call us today at 918-921-2100 to schedule a test drive and see for yourself why this Silverado is the perfect fit for your business or personal needs.

2014 Ram 4500 Chassis Tradesman — powerful, dependable, and priced to move in Jackson, GA. This rugged workhorse combines heavy-duty capability with diesel efficiency, powered by a 6.7L 6-cylinder Cummins turbo-diesel that delivers exceptional torque for towing and hauling. Built on a durable chassis with rear-wheel drive and dual rear wheels, this Tradesman is engineered for serious job-site performance and commercial use. Inside, driver-focused amenities include convenient Remote Start for easier cold mornings and quick engine warm-up — a practical feature for busy routines. The vehicle's clean CARFAX 1-Owner history gives added confidence in its condition and maintenance background, making it a smart choice for contractors, fleet buyers, or anyone who needs reliable heavy-duty transportation. This Ram 4500 offers straightforward functionality: robust towing capability, an adaptable chassis ready for upfits, and the endurance expected from a diesel-powered commercial truck. Whether you're outfitting for landscaping, construction, towing, or fleet expansion, this Tradesman delivers dependable performance without breaking the budget. Located in Jackson, GA, this 2014 Ram 4500 Chassis Tradesman is offered at the best price in the area — a competitive value for a low-owner diesel truck with essential features and a strong service record. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and secure this powerful, value-driven work truck before it's gone.

Equipment
Start this delivery truck from inside with remote start. Good News! This certified CARFAX 1-owner vehicle has only had one owner before you. The Ram 4500 Chassis is rear wheel drive. A trailer braking system is already installed on this vehicle. Set the temperature exactly where you are most comfortable in this vehicle. The fan speed and temperature will automatically adjust to maintain your preferred zone climate. It shines with clean polished lines coated with an elegant white finish. This 2014 Ram 4500 Chassis has a 6 Cyl, 6.7L high output engine. Quickly unlock this Ram 4500 Chassis with keyless entry. Anti-lock brakes will help you stop in an emergency. With a diesel engine you will be pleased with the power, torque, and fuel efficiency gains. Electronic Stability Control is one of many advanced safety features on this Ram 4500 Chassis. The high efficiency automatic transmission shifts smoothly and allows you to relax while driving.

Packages
Cold Weather Group: Engine Block Heater. Chrome Appearance Group: Bright Grille, Bright Front Bumper. Quick Order Package 29A Tradesman: Base Door Trim Panel, 4.10 Rear Axle Ratio. Ambulance Prep Group: Electronic Monitoring Module, Voltage Monitoring Auto Idle Up System, 220 Amp Alternator. Quick Order Package 27A Tradesman: Base Door Trim Panel. Trailer Brake Control. Electronic Monitoring Module. Remote Keyless Entry. Voltage Monitoring Auto Idle Up System. Low Beam Daytime Running Headlamps. **Equipment listed is based on original vehicle build and subject to change. Please confirm the accuracy of the included equipment by calling the dealer prior to purchase.**

description:
2025 Land Rover Range Rover SE PHEV AWD Belgravia Green | 550PS | Luxury Plug-In Hybrid

Discover the perfect balance of modern luxury, performance, and efficiency in this 2025 Land Rover Range Rover SE Plug-In Hybrid (PHEV), finished in stunning Belgravia Green with a refined Caraway perforated Semi-Aniline leather interior. Powered by a 3.0L turbocharged plug-in hybrid powertrain producing up to 550PS, this Range Rover delivers smooth, commanding performance with the added benefit of electric driving capability.

This all-wheel-drive, 5-door luxury SUV features 24-way heated, cooled, and massaging power front seats, complete with power recline, ventilation, and memory, ensuring exceptional comfort on every journey. The Comfort & Wellbeing Pack and Rear Seat Convenience Pack elevate the cabin experience for both driver and passengers, while SV Bespoke wood and leather steering wheel and Natural Black Birch veneer showcase Range Rovers signature craftsmanship.

Exterior details include the Shadow Pack, 22 Style 5127 diamond-turned wheels with Satin Dark Grey contrast, black brake calipers, and illuminated seat belt buckles, creating a bold yet elegant presence. Practical upgrades such as the Interior Protection Pack, Wheel Protection Pack, and Emergency Pack ensure peace of mind and everyday usability.

With its plug-in hybrid efficiency, premium materials, and unmistakable design, this 2025 Range Rover SE PHEV represents the pinnacle of modern luxury SUVs ideal for drivers seeking sustainability without sacrificing performance or refinement.

Plug-In Hybrid (PHEV) SUV

3.0L Turbocharged Hybrid Engine 550PS

High-End Luxury SUV

Comfort
  • Heated driver and front passenger seatbacks - That's hot. Heated driver and front passenger seatbacks provide more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower back pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in heated driver and front passenger seatbacks.
Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Safety and Security
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Selective Internet access - a more focused delivery. Selective internet access allows you to tailor the features for your feed, such as sports scores, local news, or current weather. When it comes to getting what you want, selective internet access is a net gain.
  • Voice activated integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, the voice activated integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. Just tell it where you want to go, and the voice activated integrated navigation system shows you the right way.

description:
The Flagship of Luxury: 2025 Mercedes-Benz GLS 450 4MATIC in Black
Experience the pinnacle of full-sized luxury with this stunning 2025 Mercedes-Benz GLS 450. Draped in a commanding Black finish, this 4MATIC All-Wheel Drive SUV is designed for those who refuse to compromise on space, power, or prestige.

As a CARFAX One-Owner with a Clean CARFAX, this "Recent Arrival" offers the latest in Mercedes-Benz innovation with the peace of mind of a pristine history.

First-Class Luxury & Performance:
Mild-Hybrid Power: The 3.0L Inline-6 Turbo engine with EQ Boost delivers a smooth 375 horsepower, whisking you from 060 mph in just 5.8 seconds.

Ultimate Comfort: Indulge in Heated and Ventilated Front Seats, Multi-Zone Automatic Climate Control (including rear controls), and a Panorama Moonroof that spans all three rows.

Next-Gen Technology: Features the latest MBUX Infotainment with MB Navigation, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto integration.

Burmester Surround Sound: A world-class 13-speaker audio system provides an immersive, studio-quality listening experience.

Intelligent Safety: Drive with total confidence thanks to Auto High-beam Headlights, Brake Assist, Electronic Stability Control, and an Exterior Parking Camera.

Modern Convenience: Equipped with a Power Liftgate, Memory Seats, and a sleek digital cockpit that responds to natural voice commands.

Why Choose the 2025 GLS 450?
Flagship Capability: With seating for up to seven and a towing capacity of up to 7,700 lbs, its the ultimate family adventure vehicle.

Efficiency Meets Utility: Achieves a respectable 24 MPG Highway, proving that a full-sized SUV can still be efficient.

Like-New Quality: Being a 2025 model with a one-owner history, you are getting the absolute cutting edge of the Mercedes-Benz lineup.

Arrive in Style, Schedule Your Private Viewing Today!

Call or Text Peterson BMW of Boise today at 208-378-5980 to schedule your test drive!

description:
The 2026 Rivian R1S Dual Standard is a remarkable all-electric SUV that offers unparalleled performance, advanced technology, and exceptional comfort. With its sleek silver exterior and impressive electric powertrain, this Rivian is the perfect choice for the discerning driver seeking a vehicle that combines cutting-edge innovation with a refined, sophisticated aesthetic.

Key features of this exceptional Rivian R1S include:

• Navigation System
• Front and Rear Dual-Zone Climate Control
• Traction Control and Electronic Stability Control
• Heated and Ventilated Front Seats with Power Lumbar Adjustment and Memory
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Rivian Audio System with 12 Speakers
• Rear Audio Controls
• Adaptive Suspension and Auto-Leveling Suspension
• Four-Wheel Independent Suspension
• Rear Parking Camera
• Auto High-Beam Headlights
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear

Beneath the striking exterior lies a powerful electric powertrain that delivers exceptional performance and efficiency. With all-wheel drive and a single-speed transmission, this Rivian R1S provides a seamless, responsive driving experience that will captivate you from the moment you take the wheel.

The interior of the Rivian R1S Dual Standard is a true sanctuary of comfort and technology. The premium vegan leather seating, heated and ventilated for maximum relaxation, is complemented by a host of advanced features, including a state-of-the-art infotainment system, a high-end audio system, and a suite of driver-assistance technologies that ensure a safe and confident journey.

Whether you're embarking on a family adventure, commuting to work, or simply enjoying the open road, the 2026 Rivian R1S Dual Standard is the perfect companion. Its exceptional range, advanced capabilities, and refined design make it a standout choice in the electric SUV market.

We invite you to experience the exceptional performance and unparalleled luxury of the 2026 Rivian R1S Dual Standard. Schedule a test drive today and discover the future of electric mobility.
