description:
This pristine Polar White 2026 Mercedes-Benz GLE 350 4MATIC SUV is a standout example of luxury and capability. As a one owner vehicle with a clean CARFAX, its been kept in excellent condition and is ready for its next adventure. This GLE 350 4MATIC SUV comes with the peace of mind that only a Mercedes-Benz Certified Pre-Owned vehicle can offer. It has passed a rigorous 165 plus point inspection and includes an unlimited mile warranty for one year after the new car warranty ends. You'll also enjoy 24 hour roadside assistance and a 7 day exchange privilege, making every drive feel more secure.

The exterior of this GLE 350 4MATIC SUV is both elegant and bold, featuring 20 inch twin 5 spoke wheels that perfectly complement the Polar White finish. The Panorama Power Tilt and Sliding Sunroof lets in plenty of natural light, making the spacious cabin feel even more open. Practical features like the power liftgate, rain sensing wipers, and auto high beam headlights ensure that your daily tasks are as smooth as possible. With the 4MATIC all wheel drive system, you can drive with confidence knowing you have excellent traction in all types of weather.

Inside the cabin, you'll find a world of comfort tailored to your needs. This GLE 350 4MATIC SUV features the Winter Package, which includes a heated steering wheel and a heated washer system to keep you cozy during those chilly mornings. You'll stay comfortable in the heated front seats with memory settings that remember your favorite positions at the touch of a button. The 12.3 inch media display with touchscreen makes it easy to control your music and settings, while wireless charging and smartphone integration keep you connected without any messy cords.

Safety and technology are at the heart of this GLE 350 4MATIC SUV, especially with the Driver Assistance Package Plus. This suite of features includes Active Distance Assist DISTRONIC to help you maintain a safe gap from other cars and Active Steering Assist to help keep you centered in your lane. The Route-Based Speed Adaptation even helps the vehicle adjust its speed based on upcoming turns or highway exits. With the eCall emergency system and a high quality backup camera, you can feel secure every time you get behind the wheel.

This GLE 350 4MATIC SUV is a versatile and stylish choice for any driver who values quality and innovation. It offers the smooth performance of a 9 speed automatic transmission and plenty of room for both passengers and gear. From the convenience of the HomeLink garage door transmitter to the advanced MBUX navigation system, every detail has been thought of to enhance your driving experience. Its a sophisticated luxury vehicle that's ready for everything from daily commutes to long road trips. Come see why this certified Mercedes-Benz is the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

  • Bumper Cover
  • First Aid Kit
  • All-Weather Floor Mats
  • Cargo Tray
  • Wheel Locks
Convenience
  • If the vehicle detects prolonged driver unresponsiveness it will automatically bring the vehicle to a stop and turn on the hazard lights. If equipped, emergency services will be contacted.
Safety and Security
  • With this system the driver's hands must remain on the wheel at all times but can be removed briefly (for a few seconds), otherwise the vehicle will prompt the driver to put their hands back on the wheel.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
Technology and Telematics
  • Without the need for a manufacturer specific app to be installed on the smart device, the vehicle infotainment system can access and control functions of a smart device physically plugged-into the vehicle.

We've built relationships with customers and established bonds with a long list of community organizations and charities. We offer complementary loaner cars while your vehicle is in the shop. Plus, we'll pay for your Pennsylvania state safety and emissions inspection as a way of saying thank you for your business. Don't have time to visit our Volvo service center in Norristown? Not to worry, as we offer a Volvo Valet, where we'll pick up and deliver your vehicle straight to your home or office. Our history traces back to when we first began as a local tire shop. While we've since expanded considerably, rest assured you'll still receive the same professional auto service at Wynn Volvo Cars Norristown. Whether you're a longtime PA Volvo owner or first-time car buyer, we look forward to treating you to a top-tier customer service possible. Stop by our showroom to say hello today!

description:
Porsche Marin is pleased to present this well-appointed 2023 Porsche Macan S, finished in classic Carrara White Metallic over a refined Black and Mojave Beige interior. Blending sporty performance with everyday versatility, the Macan S delivers an engaging driving experience paired with premium comfort and modern technology.

This Macan S features a thoughtfully selected configuration, including a Panoramic Roof System that brings natural light into the cabin and enhances the open, airy feel of the interior. 14-way Power Seats with Memory provide excellent comfort and adjustability for both driver and passenger, while the BOSE Surround Sound System delivers rich, immersive audio throughout the cabin.

Advanced lighting and driver-assistance technologies further elevate the driving experience. LED headlights with Porsche Dynamic Light System Plus (PDLS+) offer exceptional visibility and adaptive illumination, while Surround View and Lane Change Assist provide added confidence when maneuvering in tight spaces or traveling on the highway.

Exterior details underscore the Macan Ss athletic presence, highlighted by High Gloss Black roof rails and High Gloss Black window trim, which contrast beautifully against the Carrara White finish. The result is a clean, modern look that reflects Porsches performance-driven design language.

This Macan S is an excellent choice for drivers seeking a luxury compact SUV that combines Porsche performance, everyday usability, and a well-balanced selection of comfort and technology features.

2023 Land Rover Range Rover Sport SE AWD | 360PS | Santorini Black Metallic | Caraway Windsor Leather

Experience refined performance, modern design, and everyday versatility in this 2023 Land Rover Range Rover Sport SE, now available at our Land Rover dealership in Livermore, California. Finished in sleek Santorini Black Metallic with an elegant Caraway perforated Windsor leather interior, this Range Rover Sport delivers a perfect balance of athletic capability and luxury craftsmanship.

Power comes from a 3.0L turbocharged inline-6 engine with Mild Hybrid Electric Vehicle (MHEV) technology, producing 360PS and paired with a smooth 8-speed automatic transmission. The advanced 4WD system provides confident handling and stability across a wide range of road conditions, while the Range Rover Sport platform offers responsive driving dynamics and exceptional comfort. With approximately 42,340 miles, this SE model presents an outstanding opportunity to own a well-optioned luxury SUV.

Notable Features & Packages:

• SE Trim Level
• 3.0L Turbocharged Inline-6 MHEV Engine (360PS)
• 20-Way Heated, Ventilated, and Memory Front Seats
• Power-Reclining Heated Rear Seats
• Caraway Perforated Windsor Leather Seating
• Natural Brown Walnut Veneer Interior Trim
• Ebony Headlining
• Premium Interior Protection & Storage Pack
• Wheel Protection Pack
• Rear Seat Convenience Pack
• Emergency Pack
• Range Rover Handover Pack

Technology & Comfort:

• Touch Pro Infotainment System
• Digital Driver Display
• Apple CarPlay & Android Auto
• Wi-Fi Enabled with Data Plan Capability
• Four-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Cold Climate Pack
• Hot Climate Pack
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Keyless Entry & Push-Button Start

Safety & Driver Assistance:

• Park Assist
• Blind Spot Assist
• Lane Keep Assist
• Emergency Braking
• Front Fog Lights
• Rear View Camera
• Front and Rear Parking Sensors

Exterior & Capability Highlights:

• 22-Inch Style 5127 Satin Dark Grey Wheels
• 22-Inch Full-Size Spare Wheel
• Santorini Black Metallic Paint
• Terrain Response System
• LED Headlights

If you’re searching for a Range Rover Sport SE, a luxury performance SUV, or a premium used Land Rover in Livermore, CA, this Range Rover Sport offers dynamic performance, sophisticated styling, and everyday usability.

Buy With Confidence

We are a trusted Land Rover dealership located in Livermore, California, proudly serving the Tri-Valley, Bay Area, and customers nationwide. Every pre-owned vehicle is carefully inspected for quality, reliability, and overall condition, ensuring confidence with every purchase.

Nationwide Sales Available

Not located in California? No problem. We regularly complete out-of-state transactions and can assist with remote paperwork, financing options, and vehicle delivery to buyers in any state. Our experienced team makes purchasing simple and transparent, no matter where you live.

Contact us today for additional information, personalized photos or videos, or to schedule your test drive.

description:
With an original MSRP reflecting Teslas commitment to cutting-edge electric performance, this 2024 Tesla Model X combines long-range efficiency, advanced technology, and striking design in a spacious, all-electric SUV. Finished in a bold blue exterior complemented by a refined black interior, the Model X presents a sleek, modern appearance that balances style with aerodynamic efficiency.

Inside, the cabin is thoughtfully designed for comfort, versatility, and high-tech convenience, featuring premium seating and intuitive controls that enhance both driver and passenger experiences. Teslas signature Falcon Wing rear doors provide effortless access to the second and third-row seating, while the minimalist interior layout emphasizes openness and sophistication.

Equipped with Teslas advanced electric powertrain, this Model X delivers rapid acceleration, responsive handling, and impressive range, making it ideal for both city driving and long-distance travel. The SUV also includes Teslas renowned Autopilot driver-assistance features, providing semi-autonomous capabilities for added safety and convenience. A large touchscreen interface offers control over navigation, media, and vehicle settings, while smartphone integration ensures seamless connectivity.

Combining cutting-edge electric performance, innovative technology, and spacious luxury, this 2024 Tesla Model X stands out as a highly capable and stylish electric SUV designed for drivers who demand both efficiency and refinement.

description: Experience luxury and power with the 2024 GMC Yukon 4x4 Denali. This stunning red SUV combines rugged capability with refined comfort, perfect for families and adventurers alike. Enjoy advanced features like the EcoTec3 6.2L V8 engine with 420hp, Adaptive Air Ride Suspension, Max Trailering Package, and Premium Capability Package with Active Response 4WD for superior handling in any condition. Inside, you'll find leather-trimmed upholstery, a 10.2-inch infotainment screen with Bose premium audio, wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, a Rear Seat Media System, and a panoramic power moonroof. Safety is prioritized with Front Automatic Emergency Braking, Surround View Camera System, Lane Keeping Assist, Blind Spot Safety, and Adaptive Cruise Control. The Denali Reserve Package adds even more convenience, including power retractable assist steps and a hands-free power liftgate. With 22-inch bright machined aluminum wheels and chrome accents, this Yukon stands out wherever you go. Don't miss your chance to own the ultimate full-size SUV. Schedule your test drive today!

This stunning 2024 Lincoln Navigator Reserve is a true masterpiece of engineering and design. Boasting a powerful V6 engine, 10-speed automatic transmission, and 4-wheel drive, this SUV is ready to tackle any adventure with ease. • Radio: Revel Ultima 3D Audio System w/28 Speakers

Step inside this luxurious cabin and experience the ultimate in comfort and technology. The Luxury Package includes features like the Perfect Position Seats with 30-way power adjustability and Active Motion, providing unparalleled support and customization. The Revel Ultima 3D Audio System with 28 speakers will immerse you in a captivating soundscape, while the Illuminated 1st and 2nd-row seat belts add a touch of sophistication.

Designed with your convenience in mind, the Navigator Reserve offers a wealth of advanced features. The Voice-Activated Touchscreen Navigation System and SYNC 4 Communications & Entertainment System keep you connected and informed on the go. The Panoramic Vista Roof fills the cabin with natural light, creating a truly airy and spacious environment.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and this Navigator is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. From the Lane Departure Warning System to the Rear Parking Camera, you can navigate with confidence and peace of mind.

Whether you're embarking on a family road trip or tackling the daily commute, this 2024 Lincoln Navigator Reserve is the perfect companion. With its unparalleled blend of power, luxury, and technology, it's the ultimate expression of refined capability.

description: Experience top-tier luxury and capability with this Black 2022 GMC Yukon XL Denali 4x4. Powered by a commanding EcoTec3 6.2L V8 engine paired with a smooth 10-speed automatic transmission, this full-size SUV delivers power and refinement for every journey. Inside, enjoy Jet Black leather-trimmed upholstery, a 10.2-inch GMC Infotainment System with wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, Bose premium audio, head-up display, and a customizable 12-inch digital instrument cluster. Stay safe with advanced features like surround view camera, lane keeping assist, front and rear automatic emergency braking, blind spot monitoring, and rear cross traffic alert. Comfort abounds with heated/ventilated front seats, heated rear seats, tri-zone automatic climate control, power-folding third row, and a hands-free power liftgate. Additional highlights include magnetic ride control, adaptive suspension, remote start, power retractable assist steps, and chrome roof rails. Perfect for families and adventurers alike, the Yukon XL Denali offers generous space, cutting-edge technology, and unmistakable style. Schedule your test drive today and elevate your driving experience.

This 2017 Chevrolet Trax Premier is a versatile and well-equipped compact SUV that delivers exceptional value. Boasting a turbocharged ECOTEC 1.4L engine, this Trax delivers an impressive 25 city/33 highway MPG, making it an efficient and practical choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

• Driver Confidence II Package

This Trax Premier is packed with premium features that elevate your driving experience. The Driver Confidence II Package includes advanced safety technologies like Forward Collision Alert and Lane Departure Warning, providing an extra layer of protection for you and your passengers. The Bose premium audio system delivers exceptional sound quality, while the Chevrolet MyLink infotainment system seamlessly integrates your smartphone for hands-free connectivity.

Slip into the comfortable, supportive leatherette-trimmed seats and enjoy the convenience of a power-adjustable driver's seat with lumbar support. The 18-inch alloy wheels add a touch of style and sophistication to this capable compact SUV.

With a spacious interior, ample cargo room, and a smooth, responsive driving experience, the 2017 Chevrolet Trax Premier is an excellent choice for those seeking a versatile and well-equipped vehicle. Its combination of practicality, technology, and style make it a standout in the compact SUV segment.

Don't miss your chance to experience the 2017 Chevrolet Trax Premier. Visit Killeen Certified today and let our knowledgeable sales team guide you through all the features and benefits this exceptional vehicle has to offer.

At Killeen Certified, we're committed to giving every customer a car-buying experience they can trust. Every vehicle on our lot is thoroughly inspected for quality and fuel efficiency, so you can drive with confidence. Plus, with flexible financing solutions and competitive trade-in options, we make upgrading your ride easier than ever. Conveniently located in the heart of Killeen, we're proud to offer top-rated service and a team dedicated to helping you find the perfect vehicle.

The Future of Luxury: 2025 BMW X3 xDrive30 AWD in Arctic Race Blue Metallic
Elevate your driving experience with the cutting-edge 2025 BMW X3 xDrive30. Finished in the striking and sophisticated Arctic Race Blue Metallic, this all-new generation of the X3 combines bold design with BMWs most advanced technology.

As a CARFAX One-Owner vehicle with a clean CARFAX, this "Recent Arrival" offers the rare opportunity to own the latest model year with total peace of mind.

Next-Generation Tech & Luxury Features:
The New BMW Curved Display: A stunning, seamless interface featuring a Head-Up Display (HUD) that keeps vital information right in your line of sight.

Premium Package: Fully loaded with Remote Engine Start, a Heated Steering Wheel, and the Travel and Comfort System for effortless long-distance trips.

Sky Lounge Panoramic Roof: Transform the cabin atmosphere with a massive glass roof that provides an expansive, airy feel for all passengers.

Active Driving Assistant: Equipped with ACC (Adaptive Cruise Control) Stop & Go, making highway driving and stop-and-go traffic safer and more relaxing.

Parking Assistance Package: Includes Parking Assistant Professional and Parking Assistant Pluslet the car handle the steering in tight spots while you monitor the Interior Camera and surround views.

Passenger Comfort: Keep your guests cool and private with Rear Manual Side Window Shades and Multi-Zone Automatic Temperature Control.

Performance meets Efficiency:
Efficient Power: Enjoy a spirited drive while maintaining an impressive 27 City/33 Highway MPG.

Confidence in All Weather: BMWs intelligent xDrive All-Wheel Drive system ensures maximum grip and stability, no matter the road conditions.

Be the First to Own the New Standard of Luxury
The 2025 X3 is in high demand, and this Arctic Race Blue model is a true standout on the road. With its clean history and massive feature list, it wont stay on our lot for long.

Call or Text Peterson BMW of Boise today at 208-378-5980 to schedule your test drive!

Elevate your driving experience with this 2026 Acura MDX Technology Package. Boasting a sleek silver exterior and a meticulously crafted interior, this premium SUV is designed to exceed your expectations.

Indulge in the cutting-edge features that set this Acura apart:

• Navigation system with Google built-in and a 3-year unlimited data plan
• Premium Acura/ELS Surround sound system for an immersive audio experience
• Apple CarPlay and Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration
• Panoramic moonroof for an open, airy cabin
• Heated and ventilated front seats, plus heated second-row seats, for year-round comfort
• Hands-free power liftgate for effortless loading and unloading

Beneath the sleek exterior, this MDX is powered by a 3.5L V6 SOHC i-VTEC engine, delivering a responsive and efficient performance with 19 city/26 highway MPG.

Acura's commitment to safety is evident in the MDX's comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Blind Spot Information System, Lane Keeping Assist, and Forward Collision Warning. Experience the peace of mind that comes with Acura's renowned reliability and engineering excellence.

This Acura MDX has undergone a meticulous 182-point inspection and is Acura Precision Certified, ensuring you can purchase with confidence. Enjoy the benefits of a 24-month/100,000-mile limited warranty, a powertrain warranty of 84 months/100,000 miles, and complimentary maintenance services.

Grubbs Acura Grapevine is a family-owned business since 1948, dedicated to meeting your automotive needs. Whether you're shopping locally or nationwide, we offer reliable, affordable, and fast shipping options, as well as hassle-free and competitive financing solutions for all credit types.

Come in to see us today or call Grubbs Acura Grapevine at 682-284-0031. Experience the exceptional craftsmanship and advanced technology of the 2026 Acura MDX Technology Package.

  • Cargo Blocks

  • Medic Kit
  • Cargo Net
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

This Certified 2026 INFINITI QX60 AUTOGRAPH, has a Deep Emerald/Black Obsidian exterior and an Graphite interior color. 5,101 miles. Stock Number 118337L. You can connect with us by calling . No Accidents! One Owner! Important Package and Feature Information Dark Cargo Package ($440 value)
  • Black Rear Bumper Film

  • Cargo Mat
  • Medic Kit
  • Cargo Net
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

With its blend of performance, luxury, and cutting-edge tech, the 2026 Genesis GV70 2.5T is an excellent choice for drivers who want a sophisticated and capable SUV. Visit Lee Hyundai of Fayetteville to explore this standout model with transparent pricing and exceptional service.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

description:
2024 Maserati Grecale GT AWD | Mild Hybrid | Bianco | Black Leather Interior

Experience Italian design, athletic performance, and modern luxury in this 2024 Maserati Grecale GT, now available at our Land Rover dealership in Livermore, California. Finished in striking Bianco with a refined Black leather interior, this Grecale GT delivers distinctive Maserati styling paired with advanced engineering and everyday usability.

Power comes from a 2.0L turbocharged inline-4 engine with Mild Hybrid (MHEV) technology, paired with a responsive ZF 8-speed automatic transmission. The advanced AWD system provides confident traction and balanced handling, while Maserati’s chassis tuning delivers a sporty yet refined driving experience. With approximately 11,386 miles, this Grecale GT offers an excellent opportunity to own a nearly new luxury performance SUV.

Notable Features & Equipment:

• GT Trim Level
• 2.0L Turbocharged Mild Hybrid Engine
• All-Wheel Drive (AWD)
• ZF 8-Speed Automatic Transmission
• 19-Inch Gloss Dark Thetis Wheels
• All-Season Tires
• Leather Seat Upholstery
• 10-Way Power Heated Front Seats
• Sonus Faber 860-Watt Premium Audio System

Interior & Comfort:

• Black Leather Interior
• Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel
• Power Adjustable Front Seating
• Driver Memory Functions
• Refined Italian Interior Craftsmanship

Technology & Connectivity:

• Maserati Intelligent Assistant Infotainment System
• Touchscreen Display with Navigation Capability
• Apple CarPlay & Android Auto Compatibility
• Bluetooth Connectivity
• Digital Instrument Cluster

Safety & Driver Assistance:

• Advanced Driver Assistance Systems
• Adaptive Cruise Control
• Lane Keep Assist
• Blind Spot Monitoring
• Front and Rear Parking Sensors
• Rearview Camera

Exterior Highlights:

• LED Headlights
• Signature Maserati Grille & Trident Badging
• Sculpted Body Lines with Sporty Proportions

If you’re searching for a Maserati Grecale GT, a luxury AWD performance SUV, or a low-mileage Maserati in Livermore, CA, this Grecale offers a compelling blend of Italian elegance, modern technology, and dynamic driving performance.

Buy With Confidence

We are a trusted Land Rover dealership located in Livermore, California, proudly serving the Tri-Valley, Bay Area, and customers nationwide. Every pre-owned vehicle is carefully inspected for quality, reliability, and overall condition, ensuring confidence with every purchase.

Nationwide Sales Available

Not located in California? No problem. We regularly complete out-of-state transactions and can assist with remote paperwork, financing options, and vehicle delivery to buyers in any state. Our experienced team makes purchasing simple and transparent, no matter where you live.

Contact us today for additional information, personalized photos or videos, or to schedule your test drive.

description:
Audi Marin is delighted to showcase, this Certified Pre-Owned 2024 Audi Q8 e-tron quattro dressed in Glacier White Metallic over an Okapi Brown leather interior. This all-electric luxury SUV delivers smooth, powerful performance, advanced Audi technology, and exceptional comfort with zero tailpipe emissions. This vehicle includes two key fobs and charging cables.
Prestige Package ($10,400 value)
  • Digital Matrix-design LED headlights
  • Head-up display
  • Individual contour front seats with massage and ventilation
  • Leather-trimmed dashboard, armrests, and center console
  • LED interior lighting plus package
  • Manual rear door sunshades
  • Park Assist Plus
  • Power soft-closing doors
  • Valcona/Milano leather seating surfaces
AC Charging Package ($1,850 value)
  • 19.2 kW AC onboard charger
  • Second AC charging port (passenger side)
Trailer Hitch ($750 value)
  • Factory-installed trailer hitch
Audi Beam - Rings ($485 value)
  • LED Audi rings projection from front doors
Cargo Cover ($360 value)
  • Retractable rear cargo area cover
Audi Guard Protection Kit ($345 value)
  • All-weather floor mats and cargo liner
Audi Certified Pre-Owned Benefits
  • 125+ point inspection by Audi-trained technicians
  • Audi-backed limited warranty coverage
  • 24-hour roadside assistance
  • CARFAX Vehicle History Report
Electric Performance
  • Dual electric motors with quattro all-wheel drive
  • 114 kWh battery system
  • Single-speed automatic transmission
  • Up to 285 miles of estimated driving range
  • 170 kW DC fast-charging capability
  • Adaptive air suspension
Convenience
  • Audi advanced key with power tailgate
  • Power-adjustable front seats with driver memory and lumbar support
  • Power-adjustable steering column
  • Panoramic sunroof with electric sunshade
  • Heated front seats and heated steering wheel
  • Heated, auto-dimming, power-folding exterior mirrors with memory
  • Garage door opener (HomeLink)
  • Four-zone automatic climate control with heat pump
Safety and Security
  • Adaptive cruise assist with lane guidance
  • Audi pre sense front and Audi pre sense basic
  • Audi side assist (blind spot monitoring)
  • Rear cross-traffic warning

description:
Family Luxury, Road-Trip Ready: 2023 Traverse High Country Drive your Dreams

When your life runs from school drop-off in Milan to ball games in Aurora, shopping in Harrison, and weekend getaways around Greater Cincinnati and Northern Kentucky, you need an SUV that can do it all in comfort and style. That's where Tom Tepe Autocenter in Milan, Indiana, and Car Country in Aurora, IN, and Harrison, OH come in with this stunning Carfax One-Owner 2023 Chevrolet Traverse High Country.

This Traverse High Country is built for families who want minivan practicality without giving up premium style. The 3.6L V6 paired with a 9-speed automatic gives you smooth power for merging, passing, and highway cruising, even with the whole crew and cargo on board. With four-wheel independent suspension and 4-wheel disc brakes, it feels composed and confident on winding backroads or I-275 runs into the city.

Inside is where this Traverse really spoils you. Perforated leather-appointed seating, heated and ventilated front seats, and heated 2nd-row outboard seats turn every commute into first-class travel. The 8-way power driver seat with lumbar, memory seat, and 6-way power front passenger seat let you dial in the perfect driving position and keep it saved, even if drivers rotate.

Your crew will love the 3rd-row split-bench seating and easy access through the spacious second row. Add in rear air conditioning, multiple USBs, and smart storage, and you've got a road-trip hero that makes long drives feel shorter. The Dual SkyScape power moonroof floods the cabin with light, giving everyone in all three rows a more open, airy feel on those drives across Southeast Indiana and into Northern Kentucky.

Tech and sound are pure modern Chevy. The Chevrolet Infotainment 3 Plus system with navigation, Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, and a Bose Premium 10-speaker audio system keeps you connected, guided, and entertained. Exterior and interior auto-dimming mirrors, a power liftgate, and an exterior parking camera make daily errands and tight parking lots easier and safer.

If you're shopping for a late-model, low-mileage, Carfax One-Owner 3-row SUV that blends luxury, practicality, and style, this 2023 Traverse High Country deserves a spot at the top of your list. Explore more photos, payment options, and trade-in tools at https://www.TomTepe.com/and let Tom Tepe Autocenter and Car Country help you Drive your Dreams all over Milan, Aurora, Harrison, Greater Cincinnati, and Northern Kentucky.

Key Equipment Highlights (No More Than Eight):

Carfax One-Owner 2023 Chevrolet Traverse High Country

3.6L V6 with 9-speed automatic

Perforated leather-appointed seats with heated & ventilated front seats

Heated 2nd-row outboard seats and 3rd-row split-bench seat

Dual SkyScape power moonroof

Bose Premium 10-speaker audio with Navigation and Apple CarPlay/Android Auto

Power liftgate and 20" polished aluminum wheels

Driver memory seat, power front seats, and heated steering wheel

#DriveYourDreams #ChevyTraverse #HighCountry #TomTepeAutocenter #CarCountryAurora #CarCountryHarrison #FamilySUV #CincinnatiMetro #NorthernKentuckyDrivers

This stunning model, finished in a striking Blue exterior, is a true testament to Chevrolet's commitment to delivering exceptional vehicles that exceed your expectations.

Boasting a comprehensive list of premium features, the 2024 Suburban LT is equipped to elevate your driving experience. Key highlights include:

• Navigation System
• Bose 9-Speaker Stereo Audio System
• SiriusXM w/360L
• Enhanced Driver Information Center
• Hands-Free Rear Power Programmable Liftgate

Step inside and experience the refined interior, where the Preferred Equipment Group 1LT package offers a wealth of thoughtful amenities. Sink into the heated, 10-way power-adjustable front seats and enjoy the convenience of the memory settings, ensuring your ideal driving position is always within reach.

The Suburban LT's EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine, paired with a 10-Speed Automatic transmission and 4WD, delivers a powerful and efficient performance, providing an EPA-estimated 15 MPG in the city and 18 MPG on the highway. This exceptional powertrain, combined with the Premium Smooth Ride Suspension, ensures a smooth and confident ride, whether navigating city streets or tackling rugged terrain.

Beyond its impressive capabilities, the 2024 Suburban LT is brimming with advanced safety features, including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, and Electronic Stability Control, providing you and your loved ones with the utmost protection.

As you consider your next vehicle, we invite you to experience the unparalleled versatility, comfort, and technology of the 2024 Chevrolet Suburban LT. Schedule a test drive today and discover why this exceptional SUV should be your choice for your next adventure.

2024 Lincoln Nautilus Reserve AWD

Finished in Infinite Black Metallic Clearcoat over a refined Black Onyx leather interior with Medium Light Space Gray accents, this 2024 Lincoln Nautilus Reserve AWD delivers a commanding yet serene luxury experience designed for those who appreciate quiet confidence, modern sophistication, and effortless performance.

Beneath the sculpted exterior lies a responsive 2.0L turbocharged engine paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, delivering smooth, composed power whether navigating city streets or stretching out on the open highway. Lincoln’s Intelligent All-Wheel Drive enhances confidence in changing road conditions, while the refined ride quality creates a calm, almost effortless driving experience that defines true luxury.

Step inside and you’re welcomed by a cabin that feels curated rather than assembled. The expansive digital display, premium materials, and intuitive controls work together to create an environment that feels both advanced and inviting. Every surface, touchpoint, and detail reinforces Lincoln’s focus on comfort, craftsmanship, and tranquility.

Highlighted Features & Equipment:

Reserve Equipment Group

11.1" Centerstack Touchscreen Display

Adaptive Suspension

360-Degree Camera System

Heated Steering Wheel

Heated & Ventilated Front Seats

10-Way Power Front Seats with Memory

Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel

Lane Keeping System

Blind Spot Information System

Pre-Collision Assist with Automatic Emergency Braking

Rear Parking Sensors

Lincoln Connect™ with 5G Modem

Wireless Charging Pad

Premium Audio System

Remote Start & Keyless Entry

Power Liftgate

LED Signature Lighting

This Nautilus Reserve strikes a rare balance — refined yet bold, luxurious yet practical. It’s the kind of SUV that doesn’t need to announce itself loudly, it simply makes its presence known through design, comfort, and capability. Ideal for those who want premium luxury without excess, technology without complication, and performance without sacrifice.

Whether you’re upgrading your daily drive or searching for a refined SUV that fits both professional and personal lifestyles, this Lincoln Nautilus Reserve delivers in every meaningful way.

Contact us today for additional information, photos, videos, or to schedule your test drive.

Convenience
  • The cruise control accesses camera, radar and/or GPS satellite data, to automatically determine if it should slow for a curve in the road ahead.
Safety and Security
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • With this system the driver's hands must remain on the wheel at all times but can be removed briefly (for a few seconds), otherwise the vehicle will prompt the driver to put their hands back on the wheel.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending rear collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Mobile devices can wirelessly connect to the internet through the vehicle's private mobile network.

description:
Discover the pinnacle of luxury and performance in the 2023 Mercedes-Benz GLC GLC 43 AMG® 4MATIC®. This exceptional SUV combines the power and precision of AMG® engineering with the refined elegance that defines the Mercedes-Benz brand.

Boasting a stunning array of premium features, this GLC 43 AMG® 4MATIC® is a true standout. Highlights include:

• Burmester® Surround Sound System
• AMG® Performance Exhaust System
• Wheels: 8.5J x 20" Fr & 9.5J x 20" Rr AMG® Y 5-Spk

This vehicle is a true testament to Mercedes-Benz's commitment to craftsmanship and innovation. The 3.0L V6 BiTurbo engine delivers exhilarating power, while the 9-Speed Automatic transmission with 4MATIC® all-wheel drive ensures exceptional handling and control. With an EPA-estimated 17 city/24 highway MPG, this GLC 43 AMG® 4MATIC® offers the perfect balance of performance and efficiency.

Beyond its impressive capabilities, this Mercedes-Benz GLC is meticulously maintained and certified by our team of experts. As a Mercedes-Benz Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, it has undergone a rigorous 165+ point inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty and roadside assistance program. You can drive with confidence, knowing that this GLC has been thoroughly vetted and is ready to provide you with years of exceptional service.

The attention to detail is evident throughout the cabin, where you'll find premium materials, advanced technology, and thoughtful amenities. From the Burmester® Surround Sound System to the heated and power-adjustable front seats with memory, every aspect of this GLC 43 AMG® 4MATIC® is designed to enhance your driving experience.

Whether you're seeking the ultimate in performance, luxury, or both, this 2023 Mercedes-Benz GLC GLC 43 AMG® 4MATIC® is the perfect choice. Experience the pinnacle of automotive engineering and craftsmanship by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident that this exceptional vehicle will exceed your expectations and leave a lasting impression.

Why Choose Spokane Hyundai?
-One Price, One Promise Guarantee
No haggling - just our best market-based price, backed by a market value analysis.
-150+ Point Mechanical Inspection
Every used vehicle is thoroughly inspected to meet our high standards - if it doesn't, we don't sell it.

Not the right fit? Exchange it for something else - no questions asked.

Get approved in under 30 minutes with a full credit report and explanation - no pressure, no cost.
-Flexible Financing Options
We partner with local credit unions and national banks to give you the best financing choices.
 
2023 BMW X5 xDrive40i - Refined performance & AWD confidence for Spokane and the Inland Northwest
Why It Stands Out
BMW xDrive all-wheel drive delivers confident traction for Spokane winters, wet roads, and mountain drives toward Mt. Spokane or Lookout Pass.

Smooth, powerful turbocharged performance provides responsive acceleration for I-90 commuting and highway passing.

Premium midsize SUV design blends athletic driving dynamics with everyday comfort and versatility.

Upscale interior and refined ride quality make this X5 ideal for both daily driving and longer Inland Northwest road trips.

Tech & Connectivity
Large digital display with BMW's intuitive infotainment system keeps navigation, media, and vehicle settings easy to manage.

Apple CarPlay and Android Auto support seamless smartphone integration for calls, music, and navigation.

Backup camera and advanced parking assistance features help when maneuvering in tight downtown Spokane areas.

Comfort & Convenience
Leather-trimmed seating provides premium comfort for front and rear passengers.

Power-adjustable front seats help drivers quickly find an ideal seating position for longer drives.

Spacious cargo area and split-folding rear seats offer flexibility for groceries, luggage, or weekend gear.

Safety & Confidence
Forward collision warning, lane departure warning, and blind-spot monitoring help enhance awareness in busy Spokane traffic.

All-wheel drive and stability control support confident handling on snow-covered, wet, or uneven roads.

Solid BMW engineering delivers a secure, composed driving feel in changing weather conditions.

Vehicle Details
Trim: xDrive40i
Seating: Two rows, seating for five
Powertrain: Turbocharged gas engine with all-wheel drive - designed for confident, all-season performance around Spokane and the Inland Northwest.

Spokane Hyundai proudly serves drivers across Spokane, Spokane Valley, Liberty Lake, Cheney, Airway Heights, and the greater Inland Northwest. Whether you're commuting along I-90, navigating city streets, or heading out for weekend trips to Coeur d'Alene, this 2023 BMW X5 xDrive40i is built for life in and around Spokane.

Frequently Asked Questions
Q: Is the 2023 BMW X5 xDrive40i good for Spokane winters?
A: Yes. BMW's xDrive all-wheel drive system provides strong traction and stability on snowy or icy Inland Northwest roads.

Q: How does this X5 perform for daily commuting?
A: Its turbocharged engine, smooth ride, and responsive handling make it excellent for daily commuting and highway driving.

Q: Does this X5 offer a luxury interior experience?
A: Absolutely. Leather seating, premium materials, and a refined cabin design deliver a high-end driving experience.

Q: Is it easy to park in downtown Spokane?
A: Advanced parking aids and a backup camera help make parking and tight maneuvering easier for a midsize SUV.

Q: Does it have modern tech for navigation and connectivity?
A: Yes. Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and BMW's digital infotainment system support everyday connectivity and navigation.

Q: Is there enough cargo space for trips or errands?
A: Yes. The rear seats fold down to create flexible cargo space for luggage, sports gear, or shopping runs.

Q: How comfortable is it for long drives?
A: Very comfortable. Supportive seating and a quiet ride make longer drives across Eastern Washington and North Idaho enjoyable.

Q: What maintenance should I consider for Inland Northwest driving?
A: Routine seasonal maintenance - tires, brakes, and AWD system checks - helps ensure dependable year-round performance.

Q: Are there any current offers or programs available?
A: Ask us about current availability and any offers when you contact Spokane Hyundai.

With an original MSRP of $123,240, this Porsche represents an exceptional blend of performance-focused engineering, luxury craftsmanship, and advanced driver technology. Finished in striking Chalk paint-to-sample exterior color, originally priced at $3,150, the vehicle makes a bold and sophisticated statement. The SportDesign Package in Black, originally priced at $5,660, enhances the exterior with aggressive styling elements, while the 21-inch RS Spyder Design wheels, originally priced at $2,710, add a commanding stance and athletic presence. LED Matrix Design headlights with Porsche Dynamic Light System Plus provide outstanding visibility and a distinctive lighting signature.

The interior is equally impressive, featuring refined materials and thoughtful design throughout. The cabin is accented by an Olive Gray interior trim package, originally priced at $1,000, along with a Race-Tex headliner, originally priced at $1,690, creating a performance-inspired yet luxurious atmosphere. Dark Silver brushed aluminum illuminated door sills, originally priced at $1,020, add a subtle premium touch. Adaptive sport seats deliver excellent support and comfort, complemented by heated front and rear seats and ventilated front seats for year-round comfort. Four-zone automatic climate control ensures personalized comfort for all passengers, while ambient interior lighting enhances the cabin ambiance.

This vehicle is exceptionally well equipped with the Premium Package Plus, originally priced at $7,180, adding high-end comfort and convenience features such as a head-up display, soft-close doors, wireless smartphone charging, and Comfort Access for effortless entry. The Assistance Package, originally priced at $6,250, brings cutting-edge safety and driver-support technologies, including Porsche InnoDrive with adaptive cruise control, lane change assist, and Night Vision Assist, offering enhanced confidence in a wide range of driving conditions.

Experience the Pinnacle of Luxury and Performance with the 2021 Cadillac Escalade Sport in Shadow Metallic
Step into the world of unparalleled luxury and commanding performance with the 2021 Cadillac Escalade Sport. This majestic SUV, cloaked in a sophisticated Shadow Metallic finish, is designed for those who demand the very best. Under the hood, the robust 6.2L V8 engine delivers a thrilling drive, seamlessly paired with a 10-speed automatic transmission for smooth, responsive handling.
Safety is paramount, with features like Blind Spot Monitor, Lane Keeping Assist, and Front Collision Mitigation ensuring peace of mind on every journey. The Escalade&rsquor,s advanced technology suite includes a Heads-Up Display and an Aerial View Display System, offering an intuitive driving experience. For those who appreciate the finer things, the interior is a haven of comfort with leather seats, heated and cooled front seating, and a panoramic roof that invites the outside in.
Whether navigating city streets or embarking on a cross-country adventure, the Escalade&rsquor,s Active Suspension and Four-Wheel Drive provide unmatched stability and control. With a suite of premium features like a hands-free liftgate, remote engine start, and a premium sound system, this Escalade is more than just a vehicle—it&rsquor,s a statement of style and sophistication.
Be sure to call or visit Arrowhead Cadillac to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!‌

description:
2021 Range Rover Westminster Timeless Luxury with Modern Performance

The 2021 Range Rover Westminster embodies everything the Range Rover name represents: unmatched refinement, commanding presence, and effortless capability. Powered by a smooth and responsive 3.0L inline-6 engine with 4WD, this Westminster delivers confident performance paired with the legendary comfort that defines the Range Rover experience.

Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury. 20-way heated and cooled front bucket seats provide exceptional comfort in any season, while rear air conditioning ensures passengers in every row enjoy a first-class ride. The interior is beautifully finished with premium materials and thoughtful details, creating an atmosphere that feels both elegant and welcoming.

Technology and entertainment are equally impressive. The 19-speaker, 825-watt Meridian Surround Sound System delivers rich, immersive audio, while InControl Navigation Pro, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto keep you seamlessly connected. The expansive power moonroof floods the cabin with natural light, enhancing the open, airy feel that sets the Range Rover apart.

With adaptive suspension and auto-leveling air suspension, the Westminster glides over the road with remarkable composure, whether cruising through the city or embarking on a long highway journey. Finished with 21 7 split-spoke gloss silver wheels, it carries a sophisticated yet authoritative stance that never goes unnoticed.

Backed by a CARFAX One-Owner history and Clean CARFAX, this Range Rover Westminster is an exceptional opportunity to own a true luxury SUV that blends tradition, technology, and everyday usability.

Luxury Highlights

3.0L Inline-6 | 4WD

Adaptive & Auto-Leveling Air Suspension

20-Way Heated & Cooled Front Seats

Rear Air Conditioning

825W Meridian Surround Sound (19 Speakers)

InControl Navigation Pro

Apple CarPlay & Android Auto

Power Moonroof

21 Gloss Silver Wheels

CARFAX One-Owner | Clean CARFAX

Proudly Serving Maricopa, Tempe, Chandler, Surprise, Phoenix, Scottsdale, Tucson, Mesa, Flagstaff, Prescott, Sedona & Payson.
Please call for availability new arrivals come in daily and may not yet be listed online.

Elevate your driving experience with the stunning 2021 Lincoln Navigator L L Black Label. This exceptional SUV is a true testament to luxury and performance, offering an unparalleled blend of style, comfort, and cutting-edge technology.

• EXCLUSIVE BEAVER CERTIFIED 7Year/100,000 Powertrain and 12 mos/12,000 mile Bumper to Bumper Included
• Apple CarPlay
• Sunroof/Moonroof/Roof
• Leather Interior
• Bluetooth Handsfree
• Rear View Camera

This Navigator L Black Label is more than just a vehicle, it's a statement of refined sophistication. Boasting a commanding presence on the road, its bold exterior features a unique Black Painted Roof, Black Painted Cap Sideview Mirrors, and a Distinctive Black Mesh Grille that exude an air of confidence and exclusivity.

Step inside and be enveloped in a world of unparalleled luxury. The Venetian Leather Heated and Ventilated Captain's Chairs provide unrivaled comfort, while the Voice-Activated Touchscreen Navigation System and SYNC 3 Communications & Entertainment System keep you connected and in control. The Panoramic Vista Roof floods the cabin with natural light, creating an airy and spacious ambiance.

Beneath the elegant exterior lies a powerful heart. Equipped with a V6 engine and 4-Wheel Drive, this Navigator L Black Label delivers exceptional performance and capability, ensuring a smooth and confident ride, whether navigating city streets or exploring the open road.

This vehicle has been meticulously inspected and certified by our team of experts, giving you the peace of mind that comes with a BEAVER CERTIFIED pre-owned purchase. With a 7-year/100,000-mile powertrain warranty and a 12-month/12,000-mile bumper-to-bumper warranty, you can drive with confidence, knowing that your investment is protected.

Experience the ultimate in luxury, performance, and innovation with the 2021 Lincoln Navigator L L Black Label. Visit our showroom today and discover the true meaning of refined sophistication behind the wheel.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2021 GMC Yukon XL Denali. This premium SUV boasts a commanding presence on the road, combining unparalleled luxury, advanced technology, and impressive capabilities to meet the demands of the discerning driver.

Packed with a wealth of premium features, this Yukon XL Denali is a true standout. Highlights include:
• Denali Premium Package
• Pearl Beige Metallic exterior
• Tan interior

Step inside and be captivated by the Yukon XL Denali's refined cabin, where every detail has been meticulously crafted to provide the ultimate in comfort and convenience. Sink into the plush, heated and ventilated leather seats, and let the Bose 14-speaker surround sound system envelop you in rich, immersive audio. The panoramic power sunroof floods the interior with natural light, creating an airy and spacious ambiance.

Beneath the hood, the Yukon XL Denali's powerful EcoTec3 6.2L V8 engine delivers exceptional performance, seamlessly paired with a smooth-shifting 10-speed automatic transmission. Magnetic Ride Control suspension ensures a poised and composed ride, while the rear-wheel-drive configuration provides confident handling and control.

This Yukon XL Denali is packed with advanced technology to enhance your driving experience. The Head-Up Display projects vital information directly into your line of sight, keeping you informed without distracting from the road. Adaptive Cruise Control and Automatic Emergency Braking provide added peace of mind, while the Surround Vision camera system offers a comprehensive view of your surroundings.

With its spacious and versatile interior, the Yukon XL Denali can accommodate your family, friends, and all their gear with ease. The power-folding third-row seats and power liftgate make loading and unloading a breeze, while the Hands-Free Power Programmable Rear Liftgate adds a touch of convenience.

This 2021 GMC Yukon XL Denali is a true masterpiece of engineering and design, offering a driving experience that is both luxurious and capable. Visit our showroom today to experience the unparalleled comfort, technology, and performance of this exceptional SUV for yourself.

This 2021 Porsche Cayenne S, has a White exterior and a Black/Mojave Beige interior color. Please call us at 561-529-3101 and reference stock number BK9897. WHY THIS VEHICLE? Important Package Information: Convenience
  • Cruise control maintains a preset vehicle speed, automatically increasing or decreasing throttle to maintain that speed.
Safety and Security
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
  • The vehicle is equipped with sensors which compare vehicle speed to available distance to the vehicle ahead. If the speed exceeds the required distance to stop before colliding with the vehicle ahead, the brakes are automatically readied for maximum braking force once the driver applies the brakes.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile devices can wirelessly connect to the internet through the vehicle's private mobile network.

description:
2021 Cadillac Escalade Premium Luxury — Iconic Presence, Elevated Refinement
Make a commanding impression in the 2021 Cadillac Escalade Premium Luxury, finished in striking Dark Moon Blue Metallic and complemented by a rich Brandy interior with very dark atmosphere accents. This full-size luxury SUV blends powerful performance, cutting-edge technology, and first-class comfort in a bold, unmistakable design.
Key Features:
6.2L V8 Engine – 420 horsepower delivering confident acceleration, smooth cruising, and impressive towing capability.
10-Speed Automatic Transmission – Seamless, refined shifting for responsive and efficient performance.
Magnetic Ride Control™ with Air Ride Adaptive Suspension – Continuously adapts to road conditions for an exceptionally smooth ride.
22-Inch Premium Alloy Wheels – Bold, upscale styling that enhances the Escalade’s commanding road presence.
Dark Moon Blue Metallic Exterior – Deep, sophisticated finish highlighting the Escalade’s iconic stance.
Brandy Leather Interior with Very Dark Atmosphere Accents – Rich materials and dramatic contrast create a refined, modern cabin.
Curved OLED Display System – 38-inch total digital display with stunning clarity for navigation and infotainment.
AKG Studio® 19-Speaker Premium Audio System with Bose® – Immersive, concert-quality sound throughout the cabin.
Advanced Driver Assistance Features – Adaptive Cruise Control, Forward Collision Alert, Automatic Emergency Braking, Lane Keep Assist, and more.
Tri-Zone Automatic Climate Control – Personalized comfort for front and rear passengers.
Panoramic Power Sunroof – Expands the cabin with natural light and an open, airy feel.
Power Hands-Free Liftgate – Easy access to expansive cargo space.
Surround Vision Camera System – 360-degree visibility for confident parking and maneuvering.
With unmistakable design, advanced technology, and Cadillac’s hallmark luxury, the 2021 Escalade Premium Luxury sets the standard for full-size SUVs.
Now available at Randy Marion Cadillac — where bold innovation meets uncompromising luxury.

This 2020 Toyota C-HR XLE, has a Supersonic Red exterior and an Black w/Blue interior color. 44,345 miles. Stock Number L1067079. You can connect with us by calling (407) 628-4343. Wheels: 7\' x 18\' Sport Alloy, Perimeter/Approach Lights, 2 LCD Monitors In The Front, Cruise Control w/Steering Wheel Controls, Full-Speed Range Dynamic Radar Cruise Control (DRCC), Dual Zone Front Automatic Air Conditioning, 2 12V DC Power Outlets, Toyota Safety Sense P (TSS-P), Collision Mitigation-Front, Driver Monitoring-Alert, Blind Spot Monitor (BSM) Blind Spot, Back-Up Camera No Accidents! OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

This stunning 2017 Audi Q7 3.0T Prestige quattro is a true standout in our premium pre-owned inventory. Boasting a powerful 3.0L TFSI V6 DOHC engine paired with an 8-Speed Automatic with Tiptronic transmission and quattro all-wheel drive, this SUV delivers an exceptional driving experience with impressive fuel efficiency of 19 city/25 highway MPG.

• Automatic temperature control
• Memory seat
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Power moonroof
• Power Liftgate
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Heated front seats
• Alloy wheels

Slip into the luxurious leather-appointed seating and enjoy the convenience of a power liftgate, heated front seats, and a panoramic moonroof that floods the cabin with natural light. The advanced technology features, including the Audi MMI infotainment system and Audi Sound System, keep you connected and entertained on every journey.

This Audi Q7 is the perfect blend of style, performance, and practicality. With its spacious interior, generous cargo capacity, and advanced safety features, it's the ideal choice for the discerning driver who demands the best. Take command of the road in this exceptional luxury SUV.

Discover the exceptional value and quality of this 2017 Audi Q7 3.0T Prestige quattro. Schedule a test drive today and experience the difference for yourself. We're confident you'll be impressed by the attention to detail and the seamless ownership experience.

Serving Raleigh, Durham, and the entire Triangle, Westgate Mitsubishi delivers a strong lineup of new Mitsubishis plus a large selection of used cars for every budget, all with a fast, transparent buying process.

Equipment
The installed navigation system will keep you on the right path. This 2024 Subaru Forester has auto-adjust speed for safe following. See what's behind you with the back up camera on the vehicle. Bluetooth technology is built into the Subaru Forester, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. The leather seats in it are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. The vehicle is equipped with the latest generation of XM/Sirius Radio. Our dealership has already run the CARFAX report and it is clean. A clean CARFAX is a great asset for resale value in the future. This mid-size suv offers Apple CarPlay for seamless connectivity. Rogers Chrysler Jeep Dodge Ram is committed to 100% customer satisfaction, no exceptions. We are honored at the opportunity to earn your business. Welcome to Rogers Chrysler Jeep Dodge Ram. Our team strives to make your next vehicle purchase hassle free.

Vehicle Details
2024 Jeep Wrangler Sport — Low-Mileage Certified Pre-Owned, 4WD, V6 3.6L — Lewiston, ID

Looking for the best-priced, capable off-roader in Lewiston? This certified pre-owned 2024 Jeep Wrangler Sport with only 8,887 miles delivers rugged capability and modern comfort. Powered by a dependable V6 3.6L gasoline engine and equipped with 4WD, this Jeep Wrangler handles Idaho trails and daily drives with ease.

Key highlights:
- Certified Pre-Owned for added peace of mind

- V6 3.6L gasoline engine with proven reliability
- Four-wheel drive for off-road confidence

- Hands-free Bluetooth for safer calls and audio streaming
- Satellite/XM Radio for endless entertainment

This Jeep Wrangler Sport represents exceptional value with the best price in the area. Its certified status and one-owner CARFAX report mean you get a well-documented and inspected vehicle. Ideal for outdoor enthusiasts who want dependable performance plus creature comforts like heated seats and modern connectivity.

Located in Lewiston, ID, this Jeep Wrangler is ready for test drives and immediate purchase. Don't miss this low-mileage, certified opportunity — contact us today to schedule your appointment and secure this excellent-priced 2024 Jeep Wrangler Sport.

Equipment
The vehicle has four wheel drive capabilities. Anti-lock brakes are standard on this Jeep Wrangler. Light weight alloy wheels on this unit are the perfect compliment to a stylish body. See what's behind you with the back up camera on this vehicle. Good News! This certified CARFAX 1-owner vehicle has only had one owner before you. Our dealership has already run the CARFAX report and it is clean. A clean CARFAX is a great asset for resale value in the future. This vehicle has gone through a stringent manufacturer pre-owned certification process, including a meticulous mechanical and reconditioning processes. Take the stress out of car buying with this certified pre-owned. The Electronic Stability Control will keep you on your intended path. This mid-size suv has a V6, 3.6L high output engine. The Jeep Wrangler has front air bags that will protect you and your passenger in the event of an accident. This model is equipped with front side curtain airbags. This mid-size suv is equipped with a gasoline engine. Bluetooth technology is built into this vehicle, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. Heated seats for those cold winter days are included in this model. With the keyless entry system on the vehicle you can pop the trunk without dropping your bags from the store. This unit gleams with a flashy red exterior. The satellite radio system in this mid-size suv gives you access to hundreds of nation-wide radio stations with a clear digital signal. This model is built for driving comfort with a telescoping wheel. The traction control system on this unit instantly senses tire slippage and executes minute power adjustments to maintain traction at all speeds.

Additional Information
We understand at Rogers Chrysler Jeep Dodge Ram that customer loyalty is earned one customer at a time. We want the opportunity to earn your business for life. You are always welcome to visit our showroom for a hassle free low pressure shopping experience. Rogers Chrysler Jeep Dodge Ram prides itself on being the best dealership in the industry.

      • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
      • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
      • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. description: Experience athletic luxury, advanced technology and refined performance in this 2024 Audi Q5 S line Prestige, now available at Audi West Houston. As one of Audi's most popular luxury SUVs, the Q5 blends dynamic driving characteristics with everyday versatility, making it an ideal choice for drivers who appreciate premium comfort with a sporty edge. The S line Prestige trim elevates the experience with distinctive design elements and enhanced features.The 2024 Audi Q5 S line Prestige delivers a smooth and responsive driving experience with confident acceleration and composed handling. Audi's renowned engineering provides a balanced ride that feels agile on city streets and stable on the highway. Precise steering and a quiet cabin enhance comfort, whether commuting around Houston or setting out on longer journeys. The Q5 is designed to offer engaging performance without sacrificing refinement.Inside, the cabin reflects Audi's commitment to craftsmanship and innovation. High-quality materials, modern design and thoughtful details create a sophisticated environment for both driver and passengers. Supportive seating and a driver-focused layout enhance comfort and convenience, while advanced infotainment and connectivity features keep you informed and entertained. The Prestige trim adds premium amenities that elevate the overall driving experience.Versatility is a key strength of the Audi Q5. Flexible cargo space and practical interior design make it easy to accommodate daily needs, weekend travel and everything in between. Advanced safety and driver-assist technologies provide added confidence, supporting awareness and control in a wide range of driving situations. Known for its refined performance, upscale feel and cutting-edge technology, the 2024 Audi Q5 S line Prestige continues to stand out in the luxury SUV segment.Our highly trained technicians inspected this vehicle and reconditioned it to Sonic Safety Standards. While every reasonable effort is made to ensure the accuracy of this information, please verify any information in question with Audi West Houston. Please chat, email or call today and request your VIP Appointment to enjoy the Sonic Automotive Sonic Price Experience for yourself. Visit AUDI WEST HOUSTON at 15865 Katy Fwy, Houston TX, 77094 or Call 1-888-445-6998!
